{"data":[{"date":"14:34 19/07","title":"Ng\u00f4i sao Ronaldo b\u1ecb in m\u1eb7t l\u00ean ... gi\u1ea5y v\u1ec7 sinh","type":"H\u1eadu tr\u01b0\u1eddng","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/original/2018/7/19/ngoi-sao-ronaldo-bi-in-mat-len-giay-ve-sinh.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>CR7 l\u00e0 ng\u01b0\u1eddi ch\u1ecbu tr\u1eadn trong cu\u1ed9c chi\u1ebfn gi\u1eefa c\u00e1c fan \u1edf Italy khi \u1ea3nh c\u1ee7a anh xu\u1ea5t hi\u1ec7n tr\u00ean s\u1ea3n ph\u1ea9m d\u00f9ng trong WC.</h2><div style=\"text-align: left;\">Gi\u1ea5y v\u1ec7 sinh Ronaldo in h\u00ecnh si\u00eau sao B\u1ed3 \u0110\u00e0o Nha \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c b\u00e0y b\u00e1n kh\u1eafp \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng ph\u1ed1 Napoli, Italy. Tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u00f3, ch\u00e2n s\u00fat Higuain c\u0169ng tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh n\u1ea1n nh\u00e2n c\u1ee7a c\u00e1ch b\u00f4i nh\u1ecd n\u00e0y.<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"\" title=\"\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/19/Untitled-2-2469-1531967140.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">\u00a0</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nNapoli v\u00e0 Juventus c\u00f3 qu\u00e1 kh\u1ee9 \"kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u1ed9i tr\u1eddi chung\". S\u1ef1 m\u00e2u thu\u1eabn c\u00e0ng tr\u1edf n\u00ean c\u0103ng th\u1eb3ng nh\u1eefng n\u0103m g\u1ea7n \u0111\u00e2y khi Juventus chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o ch\u1ee7 l\u1ef1c c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 l\u00e0 Higuain. M\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i tr\u01b0\u1edbc, cu\u1ed9c \u0111ua c\u1ee7a hai \u0111\u1ed9i \u0111\u1ebfn ng\u00f4i v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch c\u0169ng di\u1ec5n ra k\u1ecbch t\u00ednh v\u1edbi ph\u1ea7n th\u1eafng nghi\u00eang v\u1ec1 \"B\u00e0 \u0111\u1ea7m gi\u00e0\". Vi\u1ec7c Juventus g\u00e2y \u1ed3n \u00e0o v\u1edbi th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng C. Ronaldo ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c khi\u1ebfn C\u0110V Napoli n\u00f3ng m\u1eaft v\u00e0 v\u1ee5 in h\u00ecnh CR7 l\u00ean gi\u1ea5y v\u1ec7 sinh nh\u01b0 m\u1ed9t c\u00e1ch gi\u1ea3i t\u1ecfa.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nKh\u00f4ng ch\u1ec9 c\u00f3 C. Ronaldo, c\u00e1c c\u1eeda h\u00e0ng \u1edf Napoli c\u00f2n b\u00e0y b\u00e1n nh\u1eefng cu\u1ed9n gi\u1ea5y v\u1ec7 sinh c\u00f3 in h\u00ecnh nhi\u1ec1u CLB l\u1edbn tr\u00ean ch\u00e2u \u00c2u nh\u01b0 Bayern Munich, Monaco, Torino, Chelsea.</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"4386","checkdouble":"191598"},{"date":"16:41 19/07","title":"Alisson Becker, \u00f4ng anh ng\u1ed5 ng\u00e1o v\u00e0 vinh quang \u0111\u1ebfn mu\u1ed9n","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Italia","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/original/2018/7/19/alisson-becker-ong-anh-ngo-ngao-va-vinh-quang-den-muon.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>L\u00e0 n\u1ea1n nh\u00e2n c\u1ee7a d\u1eady th\u00ec tr\u1ec5, t\u00f4i lu\u00f4n th\u1ea5t th\u1ebf v\u1ec1 th\u1ec3 h\u00ecnh tr\u01b0\u1edbc nh\u1eefng \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i c\u00f9ng trang l\u1ee9a. Trong b\u00e0i ki\u1ec3m tra d\u1eady th\u00ec, trong khi c\u1ea3 \u0111\u1ed9i \u0111\u1ea1t m\u1ee9c n\u0103m (cao nh\u1ea5t), t\u00f4i v\u1eabn l\u1eb9t \u0111\u1eb9t t\u1ea1i m\u1ee9c hai. D\u1ea7n xu\u1ea5t hi\u1ec7n nh\u1eefng nghi v\u1ea5n v\u1ec1 t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai b\u1ea3n th\u00e2n. L\u00e0 m\u1ed9t th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n, \u0111i\u1ec1u ki\u1ec7n c\u1ea7n l\u00e0 chi\u1ec1u cao, s\u1ee9c b\u1eadt, t\u00f4i \u0111i\u1ec1u thi\u1ebfu. \u0110i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3 khi\u1ebfn t\u00f4i b\u1ecb \u201c\u0111\u00e0y \u1ea3i\u201d tr\u00ean b\u0103ng gh\u1ebf d\u1ef1 b\u1ecb trong th\u1eddi gian d\u00e0i.</h2><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong>\u0110\u1ec3 t\u00f4i nh\u1edb xem! \u0110\u00f3 l\u00e0 n\u0103m 1998, l\u00fac \u0111\u00f3 t\u00f4i tr\u00f2n n\u0103m tu\u1ed5i, \u00f4ng anh Muriel th\u00ec 10 tu\u1ed5i. T\u00f4i v\u00e0 \u1ed5ng c\u00f9ng xem tr\u1eadn b\u00e1n k\u1ebft World Cup 1998 gi\u1eefa Brazil v\u00e0 H\u00e0 Lan t\u1ea1i nh\u00e0 d\u00ec. B\u1ea1n bi\u1ebft kh\u00f4ng? B\u00e0 d\u00ec qu\u00fd h\u00f3a c\u1ee7a t\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb h\u1eb3n m\u1ed9t b\u1eefa ti\u1ec7c t\u1eeb khi tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u c\u00f2n ch\u01b0a di\u1ec5n ra.</strong><br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Alisson Becker, \u00f4ng anh ng\u1ed5 ng\u00e1o v\u00e0 vinh quang \u0111\u1ebfn mu\u1ed9n h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Alisson Becker, \u00f4ng anh ng\u1ed5 ng\u00e1o v\u00e0 vinh quang \u0111\u1ebfn mu\u1ed9n h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/19/al.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>Alisson Becker, \u00f4ng anh ng\u1ed5 ng\u00e1o v\u00e0 vinh quang \u0111\u1ebfn mu\u1ed9n</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Khi tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u k\u00e9o \u0111\u1ebfn lo\u1ea1t s\u00fat lu\u00e2n l\u01b0u, cha v\u00e0 d\u01b0\u1ee3ng c\u1ee7a t\u00f4i kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 ng\u1ed3i y\u00ean, hai ng\u01b0\u1eddi h\u1ecd c\u1ee9 nh\u1ea3y nh\u00f3t tr\u01b0\u1edbc m\u00e0n h\u00ecnh TV nh\u01b0 m\u1ea5t tr\u00ed. M\u1ecdi chuy\u1ec7n tr\u1edf n\u00ean \u0111i\u00ean kh\u00f9ng khi Taffarel c\u1ea3n ph\u00e1 th\u00e1nh c\u00f4ng c\u00fa s\u00fat \u0111\u1ecbnh m\u1ec7nh. Cha t\u00f4i phi m\u1ed9t m\u1ea1ch t\u1eeb ph\u00f2ng kh\u00e1ch v\u00e0o nh\u00e0 b\u1ebfp v\u00e0 v\u1ea5p ng\u00e3. May thay chi\u1ebfc b\u00e1nh kem tr\u00ean b\u00e0n \u0111\u00e3 c\u1ee9u cho nhan s\u1eafc c\u1ee7a \u00f4ng m\u1ed9t pha tr\u00f4ng th\u1ea5y.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Cha t\u00f4i kh\u00f4ng d\u1eebng l\u1ea1i, \u00f4ng v\u1eabn mang khu\u00f4n m\u1eb7t \u0111\u1ea7y kem ch\u1ea1y kh\u1eafp nh\u00e0, reo h\u00f2:<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&ldquo;Ch\u00fang ta v\u00e0o chung k\u1ebft r\u1ed3i! Ch\u00fang ta v\u00e0o chung k\u1ebft r\u1ed3i!&rdquo;.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Trong m\u1eaft t\u00f4i l\u00fac \u0111\u1ea5y, \u00f4ng l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t g\u00e3 \u0111i\u00ean d\u1ec5 th\u01b0\u01a1ng nh\u1ea5t tr\u1ea7n \u0111\u1eddi.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">C\u00f2n t\u00f4i sao? B\u1eadn c\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u1ebfn n\u1ed7i qu\u00ean tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u lu\u00f4n.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Hai m\u01b0\u01a1i n\u0103m sau, qu\u00fd t\u1eed c\u1ee7a \u00f4ng \u0111\u1ea1i di\u1ec7n Brazil thi \u0111\u1ea5u m\u1ed9t k\u1ef3 World Cup. N\u00f3i v\u1ec1 t\u00ednh c\u00e1ch, t\u00f4i th\u1eeba h\u01b0\u1edfng m\u1ed9t t\u00ed &ldquo;\u0111i\u00ean&rdquo; c\u1ee7a \u00f4ng. B\u1ea1n th\u1ea5y t\u00f4i lu\u00f4n b\u00ecnh t\u0129nh khi ch\u01a1i b\u00f3ng sao? Kh\u00f4ng, kh\u00f4ng, gi\u1ea3 v\u1edd th\u00f4i. C\u00f3 m\u1ed9t b\u1ea3n b\u00e1o c\u00e1o v\u1ec1 t\u00f4i khi c\u00f2n l\u00e0 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 nh\u00ed c\u00f3 ghi:<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&ldquo;Alisson Becker: th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n, b\u1ea3y tu\u1ed5i.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">L\u00f9n. D\u1ec5 n\u1ed5i n\u00f3ng. D\u1ec5 kh\u00f3c nh\u00e8.&rdquo;<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">C\u00f3 th\u1ec3 b\u1ea1n kh\u00f4ng tin \u0111\u00e2u, nh\u01b0ng n\u00f3 l\u00e0 s\u1ef1 th\u1eadt \u0111\u1ea5y. T\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 ph\u1ea3i tr\u1ea3i qua m\u1ed9t ch\u1eb7ng \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng d\u00e0i \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u1ee9ng trong khung g\u1ed7 \u0111\u1ed9i tuy\u1ec3n qu\u1ed1c gia.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Tinh huong Alisson cuu thua xuat than\" title=\"T\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng Alisson c\u1ee9u thua xu\u1ea5t th\u1ea7n\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/2/alisson.JPG\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>T\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng Alisson c\u1ee9u thua xu\u1ea5t th\u1ea7n</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">N\u00f3i v\u1ec1 s\u1ef1 nghi\u1ec7p, kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 kh\u00f4ng nh\u1eafc \u0111\u1ebfn \u1ea3nh h\u01b0\u1edfng t\u1eeb \u00f4ng anh Muriel. Muriel h\u01a1n t\u00f4i n\u0103m tu\u1ed5i, c\u0169ng l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n, \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 l\u00ed do \u1ed5ng lu\u00f4n khi\u1ebfn t\u00f4i &ldquo;n\u00f3ng m\u1eb7t&rdquo;. Muriel lu\u00f4n t\u00ecm c\u00e1ch ch\u1ecdc t\u00f4i ph\u00e1t kh\u00f3c. C\u00f3 l\u1ebd \u00f4ng anh trai n\u00e0o tr\u00ean \u0111\u1eddi c\u0169ng gi\u1ecfi tr\u00f2 b\u1eaft n\u1ea1t. Song nh\u00ecn v\u00e0o m\u1eb7t t\u00edch c\u1ef1c, Muriel gi\u00fap t\u00f4i ki\u1ec1m ch\u1ebf c\u1ea3m x\u00fac, kh\u00f4ng ng\u01b0\u1eddi l\u1edbn n\u00e0o th\u00edch kh\u00f3c nh\u00e8 c\u1ea3, \u0111\u00fang kh\u00f4ng?<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Cho \u0111\u1ebfn sau n\u00e0y t\u00f4i m\u1edbi ng\u1ed9 ra, Muriel ch\u00ednh l\u00e0 ng\u01b0\u1eddi d\u1eabn l\u1ed1i t\u00f4i \u0111\u1ebfn th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">M\u1ecdi ng\u01b0\u1eddi th\u01b0\u1eddng b\u1ea3o t\u00f4i th\u1eeba h\u01b0\u1edfng gene th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n di truy\u1ec1n t\u1eeb gia \u0111\u00ecnh. M\u1eb9 t\u00f4i t\u1eebng l\u00e0 th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n trong \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng n\u00e9m th\u1eddi h\u1ecdc sinh. \u00d4ng c\u1ed1 t\u00f4i t\u1eebng b\u1eaft g\u00f4n cho \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng nghi\u1ec7p d\u01b0 t\u1ea1i th\u1ecb tr\u1ea5n Novo Hamburgo. Cha t\u00f4i gi\u1eef khung th\u00e0nh cho \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng c\u00f4ng ty. V\u00e0 \u00f4ng anh \u0111\u00e1ng gh\u00e9t n\u1eefa. \u0110\u00e2y h\u1eb3n l\u00e0 k\u1ebf ho\u1ea1ch c\u1ee7a Ch\u00faa r\u1ed3i.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">L\u00fac n\u0103m tu\u1ed5i, anh em t\u00f4i hay xem ra s\u00e2n xem cha t\u00f4i ch\u01a1i b\u00f3ng c\u00f9ng \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng c\u00f4ng ty. T\u00f4i \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng v\u1edbi phong th\u00e1i &ldquo;hoang d\u00e3&rdquo; pha ch\u00fat &ldquo;\u0111i\u00ean&rdquo; c\u1ee7a \u00f4ng. Kh\u00f4ng gi\u1ed1ng nhi\u1ec1u th\u1ee7 th\u00e0nh, \u00f4ng lao th\u1eb3ng v\u00e0o ch\u00e2n \u0111\u1ed1i ph\u01b0\u01a1ng b\u1eaft b\u00f3ng khi h\u1ecd ti\u1ebfp c\u1eadn khung th\u00e0nh. Khi \u0111\u00f3 t\u00f4i ch\u1ec9 mu\u1ed1n n\u00f3i v\u1edbi nh\u1eefng \u0111\u1ee9a tr\u1ebb xung quanh: &ldquo;Cha tao \u0111\u1ea5y! R\u1ed3i tao s\u1ebd b\u1eaft b\u00f3ng hay nh\u01b0 \u1ed5ng!&rdquo;.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">V\u00e0 r\u1ed3i Muriel k\u00e9o t\u00f4i v\u00e0o nh\u1eefng tr\u1eadn b\u00f3ng v\u1edbi b\u1ea1n c\u1ee7a \u1ed5ng. Tuy\u1ec7t! G\u00e3 n\u00e0o c\u0169ng to cao&hellip;\u0111\u1ee9a l\u00f9n nh\u1ea5t (t\u00f4i) m\u1eb7c \u0111\u1ecbnh b\u1eaft g\u00f4n. D\u00f9 kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 s\u1ef1 l\u1ef1a ch\u1ecdn nh\u01b0ng t\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 &ldquo;b\u00e9n duy\u00ean&rdquo; v\u1edbi v\u1ecb tr\u00ed tr\u1ea5n gi\u1eef khung g\u1ed7 t\u1eeb \u0111\u00f3.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Alisson\" title=\"Alisson\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/19/Klopp-phat-bieu-ve-Liverpool-va-mo-vo-doi-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>&nbsp;</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u0110\u1ebfn n\u0103m 2002, World Cup t\u1ed5 ch\u1ee9c t\u1ea1i H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c v\u00e0 Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n. Anh em t\u00f4i ng\u00e0y n\u00e0o c\u0169ng d\u1eady t\u1eeb l\u00fac b\u00ecnh minh, chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb socola, b\u00e1nh ng\u00f4, s\u1eefa v\u00e0 m\u1edf TV xem b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1. B\u1ea1n bi\u1ebft \u0111\u1ea5y, Brazil \u0111\u00e3 v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch. T\u00f4i kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 qu\u00ean \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c c\u1ea3m gi\u00e1c l\u1ea1 l\u00f9ng \u0111\u00f3, gi\u1ed1ng nh\u01b0 t\u00ecm \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c s\u1ef1 gi\u00e1c ng\u1ed9 trong vui s\u01b0\u1edbng v\u1eady.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&ldquo;M\u00ecnh s\u1ebd l\u00e0m \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c! M\u00ecnh s\u1ebd thi \u0111\u1ea5u cho Brazil! M\u00ecnh s\u1ebd \u0111\u1ebfn World Cup v\u00e0 tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh nh\u00e0 v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch!&rdquo;.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">N\u0103m \u0111\u00f3 10 tu\u1ed5i, l\u1ea7n \u0111\u1ea7u trong \u0111\u1eddi t\u00f4i khao kh\u00e1t m\u00e3nh li\u1ec7t m\u1ed9t th\u1ee9 \u0111\u1ebfn th\u1ebf. T\u00f4i lu\u00f4n gi\u00e0nh b\u1eaft g\u00f4n trong m\u1ed7i tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u tr\u00ean con ph\u1ed1 Novo Hamburgo. Khi kinh t\u1ebf gia \u0111\u00ecnh c\u1ea3i thi\u1ec7n, cha b\u00e1n c\u0103n h\u1ed9, ch\u00fang t\u00f4i chuy\u1ec3n \u0111\u1ebfn c\u0103n nh\u00e0 m\u1edbi. Anh em t\u00f4i c\u00f3 kh\u00f4ng gian t\u1eadp luy\u1ec7n v\u1edbi qu\u1ea3 b\u00f3ng nh\u1ef1a. B\u1ecdn t\u00f4i d\u00f9ng&hellip;c\u1eeda ph\u00f2ng kh\u00e1ch l\u00e0m khung th\u00e0nh. B\u1ea1n bi\u1ebft \u0111\u1ea5y, sau \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t s\u1ef1 h\u1ed7n lo\u1ea1n.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Ch\u00faa \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f4ng nh\u1eadn nh\u1eefng n\u1ed7 l\u1ef1c \u0111\u00f3. T\u00f4i gia nh\u1eadp \u0111\u1ed9i tr\u1ebb Internacional t\u1ea1i Porto Alegre, m\u1ed9t c\u00e2u l\u1ea1c b\u1ed9 x\u1ecbn t\u1ea1i Brazil. M\u1ecdi chuy\u1ec7n \u0111\u1ebfn nh\u01b0 m\u1ed9t gi\u1ea5c m\u01a1, song, gi\u1ea5c m\u01a1 d\u1ea7n tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh \u00e1c m\u1ed9ng.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><em><strong>T\u00f4i v\u1eabn l\u00f9n!</strong></em><br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">L\u00e0 n\u1ea1n nh\u00e2n c\u1ee7a d\u1eady th\u00ec tr\u1ec5, t\u00f4i lu\u00f4n th\u1ea5t th\u1ebf v\u1ec1 th\u1ec3 h\u00ecnh tr\u01b0\u1edbc nh\u1eefng \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i c\u00f9ng trang l\u1ee9a. Trong b\u00e0i ki\u1ec3m tra d\u1eady th\u00ec, trong khi c\u1ea3 \u0111\u1ed9i \u0111\u1ea1t m\u1ee9c n\u0103m (cao nh\u1ea5t), t\u00f4i v\u1eabn l\u1eb9t \u0111\u1eb9t t\u1ea1i m\u1ee9c hai. D\u1ea7n xu\u1ea5t hi\u1ec7n nh\u1eefng nghi v\u1ea5n v\u1ec1 t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai b\u1ea3n th\u00e2n. L\u00e0 m\u1ed9t th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n, \u0111i\u1ec1u ki\u1ec7n c\u1ea7n l\u00e0 chi\u1ec1u cao, s\u1ee9c b\u1eadt, t\u00f4i \u0111i\u1ec1u thi\u1ebfu. \u0110i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3 khi\u1ebfn t\u00f4i b\u1ecb &ldquo;\u0111\u00e0y \u1ea3i&rdquo; tr\u00ean b\u0103ng gh\u1ebf d\u1ef1 b\u1ecb trong th\u1eddi gian d\u00e0i.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Alisson\" title=\"Alisson\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/3/29/nong-alisson-xac-nhan-roi-roma-toi-liverpool-voi-gia-sieu-khung.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>&nbsp;</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u0110\u1ebfn m\u1ed9t ng\u00e0y, \u00e1c m\u1ed9ng th\u1ef1c s\u1ef1 x\u1ea3y ra khi Internacional chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 m\u1ed9t th\u1ee7 th\u00e0nh m\u1edbi t\u1eeb Palmeiras. T\u1ec7 th\u1eadt! M\u1ed9t g\u00e3 to x\u00e1c kh\u00e1c sao? T\u00f4i r\u01a1i xu\u1ed1ng \u0111\u00e1y c\u1ee7a s\u1ef1 th\u1ea5t v\u1ecdng khi th\u1ea5y g\u00e3.&nbsp;<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&ldquo;Tuy\u1ec7t! Gi\u1edd m\u00ecnh l\u00e0 l\u1ef1a ch\u1ecdn th\u1ee9 ba. Gi\u1ea5c m\u01a1 l\u00ean tuy\u1ec3n ch\u1ea5m d\u1ee9t r\u1ed3i&rdquo;.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">N\u1ed7i \u00e1m \u1ea3nh v\u1ec1 chi\u1ec1u cao \u00e1m \u1ea3nh t\u00f4i h\u00e0ng ng\u00e0y m\u1ed7i khi b\u1eaft g\u1eb7p \u00f4ng anh cao k\u1ec1u c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh. Muriel \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111i\u1ec1n t\u00ean thi \u0111\u1ea5u t\u1ea1i Nike Cup &ndash; gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u h\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ea7u cho l\u1ee9a tu\u1ed5i 14-15. V\u00e0 \u1ed5ng gi\u00e0nh danh hi\u1ec7u th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n xu\u1ea5t s\u1eafc nh\u1ea5t gi\u1ea3i. M\u1ed7i l\u1ea7n \u0111i ngang k\u1ef7 ni\u1ec7m ch\u01b0\u01a1ng c\u1ee7a Muriel, m\u00e1u &ldquo;\u0103n thua&rdquo; l\u1ea1i tr\u1ed7i l\u00ean.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&ldquo;Muriel, em c\u0169ng mu\u1ed1n c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t c\u00e1i!&rdquo;.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Song, t\u00f4i c\u00f2n ch\u1eb3ng c\u00f3 c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i thi \u0111\u1ea5u Nike Cup. T\u1eebng c\u00f3 th\u1eddi \u0111i\u1ec3m, suy ngh\u0129 t\u1eeb b\u1ecf b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 chuy\u00ean nghi\u1ec7p t\u00ecm \u0111\u1ebfn. T\u00f4i h\u00e2m m\u1ed9 nh\u1eefng ng\u01b0\u1eddi tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh huy\u1ec1n tho\u1ea1i t\u1eeb khung g\u1ed7: Iker Casillas v\u00e0 Gianluigi Buffon. H\u1ecd \u0111\u1ec1u ra m\u1eaft \u0111\u1ed9i m\u1ed9t khi m\u1edbi 17 tu\u1ed5i. Trong khi t\u00f4i v\u1eabn ng\u1ed3i &ldquo;m\u00f2n \u0111\u00edt&rdquo; tr\u00ean gh\u1ebf d\u1ef1 b\u1ecb, l\u00e0m sao \u0111\u1ec3 th\u1ef1c hi\u1ec7n gi\u1ea5c m\u01a1 t\u1eeb b\u00e9 \u0111\u00e2y.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Alisson va anh trai\" title=\"Alisson v\u00e0 anh trai\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/19/as.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>Alisson v\u00e0 anh trai</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Ng\u01b0\u1eddi c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng b\u1eaft \u0111\u1ea7u nghi ng\u1edd kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng ph\u00e1t tri\u1ec3n c\u1ee7a t\u00f4i. H\u1ecd ra th\u1eddi h\u1ea1n m\u1ed9t n\u0103m, n\u1ebfu kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 c\u1ea3i thi\u1ec7n, t\u00f4i ph\u1ea3i cu\u1ed1n g\u00f3i kh\u1ecfi Internacinal.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u0110i\u1ec1u k\u00ec di\u1ec7u nh\u1ea5t cu\u1ed9c \u0111\u1eddi \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u1ebfn. B\u1ea1n bi\u1ebft kh\u00f4ng? Ch\u00faa \u0111\u00e3 kh\u00f4ng b\u1ecf qua tr\u01b0\u1eddng h\u1ee3p n\u00e0y. Cu\u1ed1i c\u00f9ng t\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 d\u1eady th\u00ec, \u00fd t\u00f4i l\u00e0 cao h\u01a1n. T\u00f4i t\u1eeb 1m70 th\u00e0nh 1m87 ch\u1ec9 sau m\u1ed9t n\u0103m. M\u1ee9c \u0111\u1ed9 d\u1eady th\u00ec \u0111\u1ea1t ng\u01b0\u1ee1ng b\u1ed1n. Hu\u1ea5n luy\u1ec7n vi\u00ean b\u1eaft \u0111\u1ea7u \u0111\u1ec3 \u00fd chuy\u1ec7n n\u00e0y.&nbsp;<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">M\u1ed9t bu\u1ed5i chi\u1ec1u n\u0103m t\u00f4i 16 tu\u1ed5i, khi \u0111ang \u1edf bi\u1ec3n v\u1edbi \u0111\u00e1m b\u1ea1n. Linh t\u00ednh m\u00e1ch b\u1ea3o t\u00f4i c\u00f3 \u0111i\u1ec1u b\u1ea5t th\u01b0\u1eddng. T\u00f4i ki\u1ec3m tra \u0111i\u1ec7n tho\u1ea1i: n\u0103m cu\u1ed9c g\u1ecdi nh\u1ee1 t\u1eeb \u00f4ng n\u1ed9i. Trong ph\u00fat ch\u1ed1c, nh\u1eefng \u0111i\u1ec1u kinh kh\u1ee7ng \u1eadp \u0111\u1ebfn t\u00e2m tr\u00ed t\u00f4i.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">G\u1ecdi cho \u00f4ng, t\u00f4i nh\u01b0 ng\u1eebng th\u1edf trong kho\u1ea3nh kh\u1eafc ch\u1edd m\u00e1y.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">-<span style=\"white-space:pre\">\t</span>\u00d4ng \u00e0? C\u00f3 chuy\u1ec7n g\u00ec v\u1eady \u1ea1?</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">-<span style=\"white-space:pre\">\t</span>Nh\u00f3c, ch\u00e1u ph\u1ea3i v\u1ec1 nh\u00e0 NGAY B\u00c2Y GI\u1edc!</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">-<span style=\"white-space:pre\">\t</span>Sao \u1ea1? C\u00f3 ai b\u1ecb g\u00ec sao? C\u00f3 ai qua \u0111\u1eddi sao \u00f4ng?</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">-<span style=\"white-space:pre\">\t</span>Kh\u00f4ng kh\u00f4ng kh\u00f4ng! Ta b\u00e1o tin ch\u00e1u v\u1eeba \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c g\u1ecdi v\u00e0o U17 Brazil th\u00f4i.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">H\u1ed3n v\u00eda t\u00f4i quay l\u1ea1i sau ph\u00fat gi\u00e2y lo l\u1eafng c\u00f9ng c\u1ef1c. Tr\u1ea5n t\u0129nh l\u1ea1i, ch\u1ee3t nh\u1edb \u00f4ng r\u1ea5t th\u00edch \u0111\u00f9a, t\u00f4i c\u00e2n nh\u1eafc xem c\u00f3 n\u00ean v\u1ec1 ngay kh\u00f4ng&hellip;cho \u0111\u1ebfn khi \u00f4ng ch\u00fa nghi\u00eam t\u00fac g\u1ecdi \u0111\u1ebfn. T\u00f4i l\u1eadp t\u1ee9c ch\u1ea1y m\u1ed9t m\u1ea1ch 30 ph\u00fat t\u1eeb b\u00e3i bi\u1ec3n v\u1ec1 nh\u00e0.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">M\u1edf website L\u0110B\u0110 Brazil, c\u00e1i t\u00ean \u0111\u00f3 \u0111\u1eadp v\u00e0o m\u1eaft t\u00f4i: &ldquo;Alisson Becker&rdquo;. Ph\u1ea3i! Tuy\u1ec7t c\u00fa m\u00e8o, t\u00f4i \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c g\u1ecdi l\u00ean tuy\u1ec3n! C\u00f9ng \u0111\u1ee3t tri\u1ec7u t\u1eadp c\u00f2n c\u00f3 Neymar v\u00e0 Coutinho, hai \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh si\u00eau sao sau n\u00e0y.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">B\u1ed1n n\u0103m sau, 2013, t\u00f4i c\u00f3 tr\u1eadn ra m\u1eaft Internacional khi 20 tu\u1ed5i. 2015, t\u00f4i ra m\u1eaft \u0111\u1ed9i tuy\u1ec3n qu\u1ed1c gia. M\u1ecdi chuy\u1ec7n nhanh \u0111\u1ebfn m\u1ee9c t\u00f4i kh\u00f4ng tin v\u00e0o n\u00f3. Nhi\u1ec1u l\u1ea7n, \u0111ang trong tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u, t\u00f4i l\u1ea9m b\u1ea9m &ldquo;Wow! M\u00ecnh \u0111ang \u1edf \u0111\u00e2y. M\u00ecnh l\u00e0 th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n c\u1ee7a Brazil. M\u00ecnh s\u1ebd \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111i World Cup. Xin c\u1ea3m \u01a1n Ch\u00faa!&rdquo;.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Sau t\u1ea5t c\u1ea3 nh\u1eefng th\u00e0nh qu\u1ea3 \u0111\u1ebfn l\u00fac n\u00e0y, t\u00f4i ph\u1ea3i c\u1ea3m \u01a1n Muriel.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<div style=\"width: 100%;\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Alisson dang la muc tieu hang dau cua Liverpool\" title=\"Alisson \u0111ang l\u00e0 m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau h\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ea7u c\u1ee7a Liverpool\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/2/28/souness-phat-bieu-ve-tinh-trang-thu-mon-cua-liverpool.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>Alisson v\u00e0 Liverpool</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">T\u1eeb ng\u00e0y anh em t\u00f4i thi \u0111\u1ea5u c\u00f9ng v\u1ecb tr\u00ed cho c\u00f9ng c\u00e2u l\u1ea1c b\u1ed9, h\u1ecd lu\u00f4n so s\u00e1nh &ldquo;Li\u1ec7u Alisson c\u00f3 gi\u1ecfi nh\u01b0 Muriel kh\u00f4ng?&rdquo;. Th\u1eadt l\u00f2ng, t\u00f4i kh\u00f4ng mu\u1ed1n so s\u00e1nh v\u1edbi Muriel, v\u00ec anh \u1ea5y l\u00e0 m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau ph\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ea5u. T\u1eeb b\u00e9 t\u00f4i lu\u00f4n mu\u1ed1n gi\u1ecfi h\u01a1n Muriel, anh ta c\u0169ng th\u1ebf, \u0111\u1eddi n\u00e0o mu\u1ed1n thua c\u1eadu em bao gi\u1edd. Internacional h\u01b0\u1edfng l\u1ee3i khi c\u00f3 hai th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n lu\u00f4n ph\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ea5u t\u1eebng ng\u00e0y.&nbsp;<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">C\u00f2n nh\u1edb, khi ch\u00fang t\u00f4i t\u1eadp th\u00eam ngo\u00e0i gi\u1edd. Muriel lu\u00f4n k\u00e8 k\u00e8 v\u00e0 qu\u00e1t v\u00e0o m\u1eb7t t\u00f4i &ldquo;C\u1ed1 l\u00ean th\u1eb1ng nh\u00f3c! T\u1eadp th\u00eam n\u00e0o!&rdquo;. T\u00f4i c\u0169ng kh\u00f4ng v\u1eeba, khi th\u1ea5y \u1ed5ng m\u1ec7t, t\u00f4i tr\u1ea3 \u0111\u0169a ngay: &ldquo;Ti\u1ebfp n\u00e0o l\u00e3o gi\u00e0! Nh\u00ecn th\u1eb1ng nh\u00f3c n\u00e0y m\u00e0 l\u00e0m g\u01b0\u01a1ng!&rdquo;.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Wow, nh\u1eefng ng\u00e0y th\u01a1 b\u00e9 c\u00f9ng ch\u01a1i \u0111\u00f9a v\u1edbi b\u00f3ng nh\u1ef1a. Gi\u1eefa ch\u00fang t\u00f4i lu\u00f4n l\u00e0 s\u1ef1 ganh \u0111ua, nh\u01b0ng kh\u00f4ng v\u00ec th\u1ebf m\u1ea5t \u0111i t\u00ecnh anh em. T\u00f4i th\u1eeba nh\u1eadn m\u00ecnh may m\u1eafn h\u01a1n Muriel. V\u00ec th\u1ebf, m\u1ed7i l\u1ea7n kho\u00e1c \u00e1o \u0110TQG, t\u00f4i chi\u1ebfn \u0111\u1ea5u kh\u00f4ng ch\u1ec9 v\u00ec Brazil, t\u00f4i ch\u01a1i b\u00f3ng v\u00ec \u00f4ng anh Muriel n\u1eefa.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Muriel Becker sau khi r\u1eddi Internacional n\u0103m 2017 \u0111\u00e3 kho\u00e1c \u00e1o c\u00e2u l\u1ea1c b\u1ed9 Belenenses, B\u1ed3 \u0110\u00e0o Nha.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u0110\u1ee9ng tr\u00ean th\u1ea3m c\u1ecf c\u00f9ng \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i \u1edf tuy\u1ec3n, h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh con ph\u1ed1 h\u1eb9p t\u1ea1i Novo Hamburgo, qu\u1ea3 b\u00f3ng nh\u1ef1a v\u00e0 Muriel t\u00e1i hi\u1ec7n gi\u00fap t\u00f4i thi \u0111\u1ea5u t\u1ed1t.&nbsp;<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Muriel \u00e0, n\u1ebfu anh \u0111\u1ecdc \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c nh\u1eefng d\u00f2ng n\u00e0y, c\u1ea3m \u01a1n anh. M\u1ed7i pha c\u1ea3n ph\u00e1 c\u1ee7a em l\u00e0 d\u00e0nh cho anh. Th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng c\u1ee7a em c\u0169ng l\u00e0 c\u1ee7a anh. B\u1edfi v\u00ec ch\u00fang ta \u0111\u1ec1u l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t ph\u1ea7n trong c\u00e2u chuy\u1ec7n c\u00f3 c\u00e1i k\u1ebft \u0111\u1eb9p.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n<em><strong>L\u01b0\u1ee3c d\u1ecbch theo:&nbsp;https://www.theplayerstribune.com/en-us/articles/alisson-becker-this-is-for-my-brother<br>\r\n</strong><br>\r\n</em><strong>H\u1ea2I TH\u01af\u1ee2NG (TTVN)</strong><br>\r\n&nbsp;</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"4385","checkdouble":"191612"},{"date":"15:18 19/07","title":"Xu\u00e2n Tr\u01b0\u1eddng: U23 Vi\u1ec7t Nam kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ph\u00e9p ng\u1ee7 qu\u00ean tr\u00ean chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Vi\u1ec7t Nam","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2017/11/8/xuan-truong-u23-viet-nam-khong-duoc-phep-ngu-quen-sau-chien-thang.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 L\u01b0\u01a1ng Xu\u00e2n Tr\u01b0\u1eddng kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh r\u1eb1ng \u0110T U23 Vi\u1ec7t Nam kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ph\u00e9p ng\u1ee7 qu\u00ean tr\u00ean chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng sau nh\u1eefng g\u00ec \u0111\u00e3 l\u00e0m \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c t\u1ea1i VCK ch\u00e2u \u00c1.</h2><h2>\"U23 Vi\u1ec7t Nam kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ph\u00e9p ng\u1ee7 qu\u00ean tr\u00ean chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng\"</h2>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u0110T Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam v\u1edbi th\u00e0nh ph\u1ea7n ch\u1ee7 l\u1ef1c v\u1eabn l\u00e0 nh\u1eefng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 \u0111\u00e3 gi\u00e0nh ng\u00f4i \u00e1 qu\u00e2n U23 ch\u00e2u \u00c1 2018 v\u1eeba qua s\u1ebd chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb b\u01b0\u1edbc v\u00e0o tham d\u1ef1 \u00c1 v\u1eadn h\u1ed9i ASIAD 2018.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u0110\u1ec3 chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb cho gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u l\u1ea7n n\u00e0y, s\u00e1ng 19/7 t\u1ea1i tr\u1ee5 s\u1edf L\u0110B\u0110 Vi\u1ec7t Nam \u0111\u00e3 di\u1ec5n ra l\u1ec5 c\u00f4ng b\u1ed1 Gi\u1ea3i b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Qu\u1ed1c t\u1ebf t\u1ee9 h\u00f9ng 2018 v\u1edbi s\u1ef1 tham d\u1ef1 c\u1ee7a 4 \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng bao g\u1ed3m 23 VI\u1ec7t Nam, U23 Uzbekistan, U23 Oman v\u00e0 U23 Palestine. <o:p></o:p></p>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u0110\u00e2y \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 l\u00e0 gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u c\u1ea7n thi\u1ebft gi\u00fap \u0110T Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam t\u00edch l\u0169y kinh nghi\u1ec7m tr\u01b0\u1edbc khi b\u01b0\u1edbc ra s\u00e2n ch\u01a1i ch\u00e2u l\u1ee5c \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u01b0\u01a1ng \u0111\u1ea7u v\u1edbi nh\u1eefng \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 r\u1ea5t m\u1ea1nh.<br>\r\n<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 L\u01b0\u01a1ng Xu\u00e2n Tr\u01b0\u1eddng U23 Vi\u1ec7t Nam kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ph\u00e9p ng\u1ee7 qu\u00ean  h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 L\u01b0\u01a1ng Xu\u00e2n Tr\u01b0\u1eddng U23 Vi\u1ec7t Nam kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ph\u00e9p ng\u1ee7 qu\u00ean  h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2017/11/8/xuan-truong-u23-viet-nam-khong-duoc-phep-ngu-quen-sau-chien-thang.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td><em>Ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 L\u01b0\u01a1ng Xu\u00e2n Tr\u01b0\u1eddng</em></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Chia s\u1ebb trong bu\u1ed5i h\u1ecdp b\u00e1o, ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 L\u01b0\u01a1ng Xu\u00e2n Tr\u01b0\u1eddng cho r\u1eb1ng c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam s\u1ebd kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ph\u00e9p ch\u1ee7 quan \u1edf gi\u1ea3i l\u1ea7n n\u00e0y.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 th\u1ee7 qu\u00e2n HAGL cho hay: \"V\u00f2ng chung k\u1ebft U23 ch\u00e2u \u00c1\u00a0gi\u00fap ch\u00fang em th\u00eam t\u1ef1 tin \u0111\u1ed1i \u0111\u1ea7u\u00a0v\u1edbi c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed9i tuy\u1ec3n m\u1ea1nh. Ng\u01b0\u1eddi h\u00e2m m\u1ed9 c\u0169ng t\u1ef1 tin h\u01a1n v\u1ec1 \u0111\u1ed9i tuy\u1ec3n. Tuy nhi\u00ean sau gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u n\u00e0y n\u1ebfu m\u00e3i ng\u1ee7 qu\u00ean trong khi c\u00e1c n\u01b0\u1edbc kh\u00e1c v\u1eabn ph\u00e1t tri\u1ec3n th\u00ec ch\u00fang\u00a0ta s\u1ebd t\u1ee5t l\u1ea1i.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">M\u1ee5c ti\u00eau s\u1eafp t\u1edbi c\u1ee7a ch\u00fang em l\u00e0 c\u1ed1 g\u1eafng ch\u0103m ch\u1ec9 h\u01a1n n\u1eefa v\u00e0 c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u \u0111\u1ea1t m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau \u0111\u1ec3 kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh v\u1edbi c\u00e1c n\u01b0\u1edbc trong khu v\u1ef1c r\u1eb1ng th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng U23 ch\u00e2u \u00c1 v\u1eeba r\u1ed3i kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ea3i l\u00e0 may m\u1eafn. \u0110\u00f3 c\u0169ng l\u00e0 c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i \u0111\u1ec3 ch\u00fang em l\u00e0m \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111i\u1ec1u g\u00ec \u0111\u00f3 gi\u00fap b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Vi\u1ec7t Nam v\u01b0\u01a1n xa h\u01a1n\".<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u0110\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 v\u1ec1 c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 t\u1ea1i gi\u1ea3i t\u1ee9 h\u00f9ng s\u1eafp t\u1edbi, Tr\u01b0\u1eddng \u2018h\u00edp\u2019 cho bi\u1ebft th\u00eam: \"V\u1edbi b\u1ea5t k\u1ec3 gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u n\u00e0o, d\u00f9 giao h\u1eefu hay ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c, c\u00e1c\u00a0c\u1ea7u\u00a0th\u1ee7 \u0111\u1ec1u ph\u1ea3i d\u00e0nh s\u1ef1 t\u00f4n tr\u1ecdng cho kh\u00e1n gi\u1ea3. Em s\u1ebd c\u00f9ng to\u00e0n th\u1ec3 \u0111\u1ed9i\u00a0b\u00f3ng s\u1ebd thi \u0111\u1ea5u v\u1edbi tinh th\u1ea7n t\u1ed1t nh\u1ea5t, quan tr\u1ecdng nh\u1ea5t l\u00e0 gi\u1eef \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh v\u00e0 ch\u1ea5t l\u01b0\u1ee3ng \u0111\u1ec3 thi \u0111\u1ea5u ASIAD th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng. Gi\u1ea3i n\u00e0o c\u0169ng c\u00f3 \u00e1p l\u1ef1c v\u00e0 c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ph\u1ea3i th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n tr\u00ean s\u00e2n\".<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u0110T Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam s\u1ebd t\u1eadp trung t\u1eeb ng\u00e0y 23/7 t\u1edbi t\u1ea1i H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i. \u0110\u1ed9i s\u1ebd c\u00f3 nh\u1eefng tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u t\u1ea1i gi\u1ea3i t\u1ee9 h\u00f9ng t\u1eeb ng\u00e0y 3/8-7/8 tr\u01b0\u1edbc khi ch\u1ed1t danh s\u00e1ch ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c 20 c\u00e1i t\u00ean s\u1ebd l\u00ean \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng tham d\u1ef1 ASIAD 2018.</p>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/cong-bo-danh-sach-dt-olympic-viet-nam-thay-park-noi-ve-co-hoi-cua-thu-mon-bui-tien-dung-168-191597.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/19/cong-bo-danh-sach-dt-olympic-viet-nam-thay-park-noi-ve-co-hoi-cua-thu-mon-bui-tien-dung.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/cong-bo-danh-sach-dt-olympic-viet-nam-thay-park-noi-ve-co-hoi-cua-thu-mon-bui-tien-dung-168-191597.html\">C\u00f4ng b\u1ed1 danh s\u00e1ch \u0110T Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam, th\u1ea7y Park n\u00f3i v\u1ec1 c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i c\u1ee7a th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n B\u00f9i Ti\u1ebfn D\u0169ng</span><br>\r\nChia s\u1ebb tr\u01b0\u1edbc b\u00e1o gi\u1edbi, HLV Park Hang Seo kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i v\u1eabn chia \u0111\u1ec1u cho c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 v\u00e0 th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n B\u00f9i Ti\u1ebfn D\u0169ng v\u1eabn c\u00f3 su\u1ea5t b\u1eaft ch\u00ednh n\u1ebfu th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n t\u1ed1t.</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Minh Long (TTVN)<span style=\"font-size:16.0pt;line-height:115%\"><o:p></o:p></span></p></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"4384","checkdouble":"191601"},{"date":"15:42 19/07","title":"S\u1ed1c: Nh\u00e0 v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch World Cup 2018 v\u1eabn c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 kho\u00e1c \u00e1o Philippines d\u1ef1 AFF Cup","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Vi\u1ec7t Nam","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/original/2018/7/19/soc-nha-vo-dich-world-cup-2018-van-co-the-khoac-ao-philippines-du-aff-cup.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>C\u00e2u chuy\u1ec7n kh\u00f3 tin n\u00e0y \u0111ang x\u1ea3y ra v\u1edbi ng\u00f4i sao mang qu\u1ed1c t\u1ecbch Ph\u00e1p, g\u1ed1c Philippines Alphonse Areola. Anh ch\u00ednh l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t trong 23 ng\u00f4i sao c\u1ee7a Les Bleus \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c n\u00e2ng cao c\u00fap v\u00e0ng th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi 2018 </h2><h2>Philippines ch\u00e8o k\u00e9o nh\u00e0 v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch World Cup 2018\u00a0</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Philippines mu\u1ed1n nh\u00e0 v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch World Cup 2018 Alphonse Areola h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Philippines mu\u1ed1n nh\u00e0 v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch World Cup 2018 Alphonse Areola h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/19/GettyImages-999542344.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td><em>Alphonse Areola (ph\u1ea3i) v\u1eabn \u0111\u1ee7 \u0111i\u1ec1u ki\u1ec7n kho\u00e1c \u00e1o \u0110T Philippines</em></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align: justify;\">Alphonse Areola l\u00e0 th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n sinh tr\u01b0\u1edfng t\u1ea1i Paris, Ph\u00e1p trong m\u1ed9t gia \u0111\u00ecnh c\u00f3 b\u1ed1 m\u1eb9 \u0111\u1ec1u c\u00f3 ngu\u1ed3n g\u1ed1c l\u00e0 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Philipines. N\u0103m 2006, khi m\u1edbi 13 tu\u1ed5i anh \u0111\u00e3 l\u1ecdt v\u00e0o m\u1eaft xanh c\u1ee7a c\u00e1c tuy\u1ec3n tr\u1ea1ch vi\u00ean CLB PSG v\u00e0 gia nh\u1eadp \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng n\u00e0y. PSG c\u0169ng l\u00e0 b\u1ec7 ph\u00f3ng gi\u00fap anh tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh m\u1ed9t ng\u00f4i sao v\u00e0 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c tri\u1ec7u t\u1eadp v\u00e0o \u0110T Ph\u00e1p tham d\u1ef1 VCK World Cup 2018.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Tuy nhi\u00ean \u1edf \u0110T Ph\u00e1p, Areola ch\u1ec9 l\u00e0 s\u1ef1 l\u1ef1a ch\u1ecdn s\u1ed1 3 c\u1ee7a HLV Deschamps sau Lloris v\u00e0 Steve Mandanda. T\u00ednh t\u1edbi th\u1eddi \u0111i\u1ec3m hi\u1ec7n t\u1ea1i, th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n 25 tu\u1ed5i n\u00e0y v\u1eabn ch\u01b0a c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c n\u00e0o cho Les Bleus d\u00f9 anh thi \u0111\u1ea5u kh\u00e1 th\u01b0\u1eddng xuy\u00ean t\u1ea1i PSG.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">C\u0169ng v\u00ec l\u00fd do ch\u01b0a t\u1eebng 1 l\u1ea7n kho\u00e1c \u00e1o \u0110TQG Ph\u00e1p n\u00ean v\u1ec1 l\u00fd thuy\u1ebft, Alphonse Areola v\u1eabn c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 kho\u00e1c \u00e1o m\u1ed9t \u0111\u1ed9i tuy\u1ec3n kh\u00e1c tr\u00ean th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi. N\u1eafm b\u1eaft c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i n\u00e0y, L\u0110B\u0110 Philippines \u0111\u00e3 v\u00e0 \u0111ang ch\u00e8o k\u00e9o th\u1ee7 th\u00e0nh 25 tu\u1ed5i v\u1ec1 kho\u00e1c \u00e1o cho \u0111\u1ed9i tuy\u1ec3n qu\u1ed1c gia \u0111\u1ea5t n\u01b0\u1edbc n\u00e0y.\u00a0<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u0110\u01b0\u1ee3c bi\u1ebft, Philippines \u0111\u00e3 n\u1ed7 l\u1ef1c thuy\u1ebft ph\u1ee5c Areola t\u1eeb c\u00e1ch \u0111\u00e2y 6 n\u0103m v\u1ec1 tr\u01b0\u1edbc. L\u00fac n\u00e0y, h\u1ecd v\u1eabn \u0111ang ch\u1edd \u0111\u1ee3i c\u00e1i g\u1eadt \u0111\u1ea7u c\u1ee7a Areola, trong b\u1ed1i c\u1ea3nh anh v\u1eabn ch\u01b0a th\u1ec3 c\u1ea1nh tranh v\u1ecb tr\u00ed s\u1ed1 1 trong khung g\u1ed7 \u0111\u1ed9i tuy\u1ec3n Ph\u00e1p, khi m\u00e0 Hugo Lloris v\u1eabn th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n phong \u0111\u1ed9 c\u1ef1c k\u1ef3 \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng.\u00a0<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">N\u1ebfu th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng, Philippines s\u1ebd c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t g\u01b0\u01a1ng m\u1eb7t c\u1ef1c k\u1ef3 ch\u1ea5t l\u01b0\u1ee3ng \u0111\u1ec3 tham gia AFF Cup, gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u m\u00e0 h\u1ecd ch\u01b0a t\u1eebng l\u00ean ng\u00f4i v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nMinh Long (TTVN)<span style=\"font-size:\n16.0pt;line-height:115%\"><o:p></o:p></span></p></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"4383","checkdouble":"191606"},{"date":"16:08 19/07","title":"L\u1ecbch thi \u0111\u1ea5u giao h\u1eefu h\u00e8 2018 c\u1ee7a CLB Chelsea","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/19/lich-thi-dau-giao-huu-he-2018-cua-clb-chelsea.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>L\u1ecbch thi \u0111\u1ea5u c\u1ee7a Chelsea trong m\u00f9a h\u00e8 2018: Chuy\u00ean trang Bongda24h c\u1eadp nh\u1eadt th\u00f4ng tin l\u1ecbch thi \u0111\u1ea5u - LT\u0110 giao h\u1eefu h\u00e8 2018 c\u1ee7a Chelsea nhanh v\u00e0 ch\u00ednh x\u00e1c nh\u1ea5t.</h2><div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"L\u1ecbch thi \u0111\u1ea5u c\u1ee7a Chelsea h\u00e8 2018 L\u1ecbch thi \u0111\u1ea5u h\u00e8 2018 c\u1ee7a Chelsea h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"L\u1ecbch thi \u0111\u1ea5u c\u1ee7a Chelsea h\u00e8 2018 L\u1ecbch thi \u0111\u1ea5u h\u00e8 2018 c\u1ee7a Chelsea h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/19/chelsea-camisa-18-19-28-05-2018_vyoj6q4yttrd1pgckrgt0wjvj.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">L\u1ecbch thi \u0111\u1ea5u c\u1ee7a Chelsea trong h\u00e8 2018</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: left;\">Chelsea \u0111\u00e3 tr\u1ea3i qua m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i 2018/19 k\u00e9m th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng khi ch\u1ec9 gi\u00e0nh \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c m\u1ed9t danh hi\u1ec7u duy nh\u1ea5t FA Cup nh\u01b0ng kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 c\u00e1n \u0111\u00edch trong Top 4 Ngo\u1ea1i h\u1ea1ng Anh \u0111\u1ec3 gi\u00e0nh v\u00e9 d\u1ef1 Champions League.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nV\u00e0i ng\u00e0y tr\u01b0\u1edbc sau khi sa th\u1ea3i HLV Antonio Conte, Chelsea \u0111\u00e3 ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c b\u1ed5 nhi\u1ec7m HLV Maurizio Sarri v\u00e0o gh\u1ebf n\u00f3ng. C\u00f9ng v\u1edbi \u0111\u00f3, h\u1ecdc tr\u00f2 c\u1ee7a Sarri \u1edf Napoli l\u00e0 Jorginho c\u0169ng gia nh\u1eadp Chelsea v\u1edbi b\u1ea3n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng tr\u1ecb gi\u00e1 51,3 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng Anh.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nHi\u1ec7n t\u1ea1i c\u1ef1u thuy\u1ec1n tr\u01b0\u1edfng Napoli \u0111\u00e3 b\u1eaft \u0111\u1ea7u l\u00e0m quen v\u00e0 cho c\u00e1c h\u1ecdc tr\u00f2 m\u1edbi t\u1eadp luy\u1ec7n \u1edf London. Ng\u00e0y 23/7 t\u1edbi Chelsea s\u1ebd sang Australia \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u00e1 giao h\u1eefu v\u1edbi CLB Perth Glory. </div>\r\n<h2>L\u1ecbch thi \u0111\u1ea5u c\u1ee7a Chelsea trong h\u00e8 2018 (gi\u1edd Vi\u1ec7t Nam)</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: left;\">18h30 ng\u00e0y 23/7 Perth Glory vs Chelsea<br>\r\n01h05 ng\u00e0y 29/7 Chelsea vs Inter Milan (ICC\u00a02018)<br>\r\n02h05 ng\u00e0y 2/8 Arsenal vs Chelsea (ICC\u00a02018)<br>\r\n21h00 ng\u00e0y 5/8 Chelsea vs Manchester City (Si\u00eau C\u00fap Anh - FA Community Shield)<br>\r\n02h05 ng\u00e0y 8/8 Chelsea vs Lyon (ICC\u00a02018)<br>\r\n\u00a0</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"4382","checkdouble":"191609"},{"date":"16:17 19/07","title":"L\u1ecbch thi \u0111\u1ea5u giao h\u1eefu h\u00e8 2018 c\u1ee7a CLB Arsenal","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/19/lich-thi-dau-giao-huu-he-2018-cua-clb-arsenal.png","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>L\u1ecbch thi \u0111\u1ea5u c\u1ee7a Arsenal trong m\u00f9a h\u00e8 2018: Chuy\u00ean trang Bongda24h c\u1eadp nh\u1eadt th\u00f4ng tin l\u1ecbch thi \u0111\u1ea5u - LT\u0110 giao h\u1eefu h\u00e8 2018 c\u1ee7a Arsenal nhanh v\u00e0 ch\u00ednh x\u00e1c nh\u1ea5t.</h2>Arsenal \u0111\u00e3 chia tay HLV Arsene Wenger sau khi m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i 2018/19 h\u1ea1 m\u00e0n v\u00e0 c\u1ef1u HLV&nbsp;c\u1ee7a PSG, Unai Emery \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c l\u1ef1a ch\u1ecdn thay th\u1ebf. Nh\u00e0 c\u1ea7m qu\u00e2n ng\u01b0\u1eddi TBN \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t kh\u1edfi \u0111\u1ea7u v\u00f4 c\u00f9ng \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng khi \u0111\u00e8 b\u1eb9p nh\u01b0\u1ee3c ti\u1ec3u Boreham Wood v\u1edbi t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1 8-0 \u1edf tr\u1eadn giao h\u1eefu h\u00f4m 14/7 v\u1eeba qua.\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"L\u1ecbch thi \u0111\u1ea5u c\u1ee7a Arsenal h\u00e8 2018 L\u1ecbch thi \u0111\u1ea5u h\u00e8 2018 c\u1ee7a Arsenal h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"L\u1ecbch thi \u0111\u1ea5u c\u1ee7a Arsenal h\u00e8 2018 L\u1ecbch thi \u0111\u1ea5u h\u00e8 2018 c\u1ee7a Arsenal h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/19/ars-153114285426350670822.png\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">L\u1ecbch thi \u0111\u1ea5u giao h\u1eefu h\u00e8 2018 c\u1ee7a Arsenal</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<br>\r\nS\u1eafp t\u1edbi Arsenal s\u1ebd bay sang Singapore tham d\u1ef1 gi\u1ea3i giao h\u1eefu International Champions Cup 2018 (ICC Cup) v\u00e0o cu\u1ed1i th\u00e1ng 7. T\u1ea1i gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u n\u00e0y, Ph\u00e1o th\u1ee7 s\u1ebd l\u1ea7n l\u01b0\u1ee3t g\u1eb7p Atletico Madrid (26/7) v\u00e0 PSG (28/7).<br>\r\n<br>\r\nTour du \u0111\u1ea5u h\u00e8 c\u1ee7a Ph\u00e1o th\u1ee7 s\u1ebd k\u1ebft th\u00fac v\u00e0o ng\u00e0y 4/8 v\u1edbi tr\u1eadn g\u1eb7p Sevilla, \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng c\u0169 c\u1ee7a ch\u00ednh t\u00e2n HLV Unai Emery.<br>\r\n<h2>L\u1ecbch thi \u0111\u1ea5u c\u1ee7a Arsenal trong h\u00e8 2018</h2>\r\n21h00 ng\u00e0y 14/7: Boreham Wood 0-8 Arsenal (Hertfordshire, Anh)<br>\r\n18h35 ng\u00e0y 26/7: Atletico Madrid vs Arsenal (Kallang, Singapore)<br>\r\n18h35 ng\u00e0y 28/7: Arsenal vs PSG (Kallang, Singapore)<br>\r\n02h05 ng\u00e0y 2/8: Arsenal vs Chelsea (Dublin, Ireland)<br>\r\n01h00 ng\u00e0y 4/8: Arsenal vs Sevilla (Stockholm, Th\u1ee5y \u0110i\u1ec3n)<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/lich-thi-dau-giao-huu-he-2018-cua-clb-chelsea-172-191609.html\">L\u1ecbch thi \u0111\u1ea5u giao h\u1eefu h\u00e8 2018 c\u1ee7a CLB Chelsea</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/lich-thi-dau-giao-huu-he-2018-cua-mu-172-191607.html\">L\u1ecbch thi \u0111\u1ea5u giao h\u1eefu h\u00e8 2018 c\u1ee7a MU</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<br></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"4381","checkdouble":"191611"},{"date":"16:59 19/07","title":"B\u1ea3n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng 66 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng Alisson s\u1ebd \u0111em l\u1ea1i nh\u1eefng g\u00ec cho Liverpool?","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/19/ban-hop-dong-66-trieu-bang-alisson-se-dem-lai-nhung-gi-cho-liverpool.png","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Liverpool mua Alisson c\u1ee7a Roma v\u1edbi gi\u00e1 66 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng, ng\u00f4i sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi Brazil \u0111\u00e3 v\u01b0\u1ee3t qua Ederson \u0111\u1ec3 tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n \u0111\u1eaft gi\u00e1 nh\u1ea5t th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi. V\u1edbi t\u00e0i n\u0103ng c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh th\u1ee7 th\u00e0nh 26 tu\u1ed5i \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c k\u1ef3 v\u1ecdng s\u1ebd t\u1ecfa s\u00e1ng gi\u00fap The Kop h\u01b0\u1edbng \u0111\u1ebfn nh\u1eefng danh hi\u1ec7u l\u1edbn.\r\n</h2><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">Liverpool c\u1ea7n s\u1ef1 thay th\u1ebf cho Karius v\u00e0 Mignolet</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nGiai \u0111o\u1ea1n \u0111\u1ea7u m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i v\u1eeba qua Simon Mignolet l\u00e0 th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n s\u1ed1 1 c\u1ee7a Liverpool, HLV Klopp tin t\u01b0\u1edfng kinh nghi\u1ec7m v\u00e0 quy\u1ebft t\u00e2m ch\u1ee9ng t\u1ecf m\u00ecnh c\u1ee7a ng\u00f4i sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi B\u1ec9. Tuy nhi\u00ean, c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 sinh n\u0103m 1988 \u0111\u00e3 g\u00e2y th\u1ea5t v\u1ecdng r\u1ea5t l\u1edbn.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Liverpool mua Alisson \u0110\u1eaft x\u1eaft ra mi\u1ebfng h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Liverpool mua Alisson \u0110\u1eaft x\u1eaft ra mi\u1ebfng h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/2/12/Liverpool-mua-Alisson-Dat-xat-ra-mieng-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Loris Karius v\u00e0 Simon Mignolet kh\u00f4ng khi\u1ebfn Klopp c\u1ea3m th\u1ea5y h\u00e0i l\u00f2ng</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nMignolet li\u00ean t\u1ee5c m\u1eafc sai l\u1ea7m, anh ch\u01a1i b\u00f3ng thi\u1ebfu s\u1ef1 \u1ed5n \u0111\u1ecbnh. Ch\u00ednh phong \u0111\u1ed9 thi\u1ebfu \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng c\u1ee7a c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 30 tu\u1ed5i khi\u1ebfn Liverpool ph\u1ea3i nh\u1eadn r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u b\u00e0n thua v\u00e0 th\u1ea5t th\u1ebf trong cu\u1ed9c \u0111ua t\u1edbi danh hi\u1ec7u Ngo\u1ea1i h\u1ea1ng Anh.</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nTh\u1ef1c ra vi\u1ec7c Mignolet ch\u01a1i thi\u1ebfu s\u1ef1 \u1ed5n \u0111\u1ecbnh c\u0169ng ch\u1eb3ng c\u00f3 g\u00ec l\u1ea1 c\u1ea3. T\u1eeb khi chuy\u1ec3n t\u1edbi Anfield v\u00e0o n\u0103m 2010 t\u1eeb Sunderland ch\u01b0a khi n\u00e0o th\u1ee7 th\u00e0nh ng\u01b0\u1eddi B\u1ec9 \u0111em \u0111\u1ebfn s\u1ef1 y\u00ean t\u00e2m, anh m\u1eafc r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u l\u1ed7i d\u1eabn \u0111\u1ebfn b\u00e0n thua.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nPhong \u0111\u1ed9 t\u1ec7 h\u1ea1i c\u1ee7a Mignolet \u0111\u00e3 t\u1ea1o c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i cho Loris Karius \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ch\u1ee9ng t\u1ecf kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh. Ng\u00f4i sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0110\u1ee9c \u0111\u00e3 n\u1eafm b\u1eaft c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i r\u1ea5t t\u1ed1t khi ch\u01a1i r\u1ea5t \u1ed5n \u0111\u1ecbnh, anh tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh l\u1ef1a ch\u1ecdn s\u1ed1 1 c\u1ee7a The Kop \u1edf giai \u0111o\u1ea1n l\u01b0\u1ee3t v\u1ec1 m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i 2017/18.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nKhi \u0111ang d\u1ea7n chi\u1ebfm \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ni\u1ec1m tin c\u1ee7a Klopp th\u00ec Loris Karius l\u1ea1i m\u1eafc sai l\u1ea7m nghi\u00eam tr\u1ecdng \u1edf tr\u1eadn chung k\u1ebft Champions League 2018. M\u1ed9t t\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng n\u00e9m b\u00f3ng th\u1eb3ng v\u00e0o ch\u00e2n Benzema v\u00e0 b\u1eaft b\u00f3ng kh\u00f4ng d\u00ednh sau c\u00fa s\u00fat kh\u00f4ng qu\u00e1 kh\u00f3 c\u1ee7a Bale khi\u1ebfn Liverpool thua 1-3.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nS\u1ee9c \u00e9p d\u00e0nh cho Loris Karius l\u00e0 c\u1ef1c l\u1edbn, NHM Liverpool g\u00e2y \u00e1p l\u1ef1c bu\u1ed9c BL\u0110 \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng ph\u1ea3i mua th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n m\u1edbi.&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nR\u00f5 r\u00e0ng \u0111i\u1ec3m y\u1ebfu v\u1ec1 t\u00e2m l\u00fd c\u1ee7a Karius kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 kh\u1eafc ph\u1ee5c trong ng\u00e0y m\u1ed9t ng\u00e0y hai c\u00f2n Mignolet th\u00ec ch\u1eb3ng bao gi\u1edd \u0111em \u0111\u1ebfn s\u1ef1 y\u00ean t\u00e2m, b\u1edfi v\u1eady mua th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n m\u1edbi l\u00e0 nhi\u1ec7m v\u1ee5 h\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ea7u c\u1ee7a The Kop \u1edf k\u1ef3 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng H\u00e8 2018.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>Liverpool quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh chi 66 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng mua Alisson</h2>\r\n<h2>&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">HLV Klopp hi\u1ec3u r\u1eb1ng v\u1edbi Karius v\u00e0 Mignolet, Liverpool s\u1ebd r\u1ea5t kh\u00f3 \u0111\u1ec3 hy v\u1ecdng gi\u00e0nh nh\u1eefng danh hi\u1ec7u l\u1edbn. \u00d4ng th\u1ea7y ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0110\u1ee9c \u0111\u00e3 \u00e2m th\u1ea7m l\u00ean k\u1ebf ho\u1ea1ch \u0111\u01b0a v\u1ec1 th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n Alisson c\u1ee7a Roma. Sau m\u1ed9t th\u1eddi gian d\u00e0i \u0111\u00e0m ph\u00e1n L\u1eef \u0111o\u00e0n \u0111\u1ecf \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111i\u1ec1u m\u00ecnh c\u1ea7n.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Alisson\" title=\"Alisson\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/19/Doi-hinh-Liverpool-2018-sieu-khung-o-mua-giai-toi-hinh-anh.PNG\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Liverpool \u0111\u1ea1t \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c th\u1ecfa thu\u1eadn mua Alisson v\u1edbi gi\u00e1 66 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/bong-da-anh/nong-alisson-xac-nhan-roi-roma-toi-liverpool-voi-gia-sieu-khung-172-191549.html\" target=\"_blank\">Liverpool \u0111\u1ea1t \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c th\u1ecfa thu\u1eadn mua Alisson</span>. Theo \u0111\u00f3, h\u1ecd s\u1ebd k\u00fd h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng 5 n\u0103m v\u1edbi c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 26 tu\u1ed5i, t\u1ea1i Anfield c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Brazil nh\u1eadn l\u01b0\u01a1ng 150.000 b\u1ea3ng/tu\u1ea7n. Hi\u1ec7n ng\u00f4i sao sinh n\u0103m 1992 \u0111\u00e3 bay sang Anh \u0111\u1ec3 k\u00fd h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng v\u1edbi \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng th\u00e0nh ph\u1ed1 C\u1ea3ng.&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n\u0110\u1ec3 c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c Alisson Liverpool \u0111\u00e3 ph\u1ea3i b\u1ecf ra 66 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng. V\u1edbi s\u1ed1 ti\u1ec1n n\u00e0y, ng\u00f4i sao 26 tu\u1ed5i s\u1ebd v\u01b0\u1ee3t qua \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i Ederson \u1edf tuy\u1ec3n Brazil \u0111\u1ec3 tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n \u0111\u1eaft gi\u00e1 nh\u1ea5t th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi. C\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 sinh n\u0103m 1992 c\u0169ng \u0111\u00e3 l\u00ean ti\u1ebfng chia tay Roma.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n&ldquo;T\u00f4i mu\u1ed1n n\u00f3i c\u1ea3m \u01a1n \u0111\u1ebfn ng\u01b0\u1eddi h\u00e2m m\u1ed9 AS Roma, trong qu\u00e3ng th\u1eddi gian t\u1ea1i Olympico t\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 nh\u1eadn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c s\u1ef1 \u1ee7ng h\u1ed9 r\u1ea5t l\u1edbn t\u1eeb m\u1ecdi ng\u01b0\u1eddi, t\u00f4i c\u1ea3m th\u1ea5y r\u1ea5t vui v\u00ec \u0111i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3. Tuy nhi\u00ean, b\u00e2y gi\u1edd l\u00e0 l\u00fac cho m\u1ed9t cu\u1ed9c phi\u00eau l\u01b0u m\u1edbi&rdquo;.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>T\u00e0i n\u0103ng c\u1ee7a Alisson th\u1ef1c s\u1ef1 c\u1ea7n thi\u1ebft v\u1edbi Liverpool</h2>\r\n<h2>&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">M\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i v\u1eeba qua, th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n Alisson \u0111\u00e3 ch\u01a1i c\u1ef1c t\u1ed1t trong m\u00e0u \u00e1o Roma. Anh ch\u1ec9 \u0111\u1ec3 l\u1ecdt l\u01b0\u1edbi 28 b\u00e0n sau 37 l\u1ea7n ra s\u00e2n \u1edf Serie A (trung b\u00ecnh 0.75 b\u00e0n thua/tr\u1eadn).&nbsp;<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Liverpool cua Klopp mua Alisson\" title=\"Liverpool cua Klopp mua Alisson\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/19/liverpool-sap-co-alisson-khi-bien-chat-tao-nen-su-vi-dai.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Alisson s\u1ebd l\u00e0 s\u1ef1 b\u1ed5 sung ch\u1ea5t l\u01b0\u1ee3ng cho Liverpool</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nS\u1ed1 l\u1ea7n c\u1ee9u thua c\u1ee7a Alisson v\u01b0\u1ee3t tr\u1ed9i so v\u1edbi Karius v\u00e0 Mignolet, theo \u0111\u00f3 trung b\u00ecnh anh c\u1ee9u thua 2.89 l\u1ea7n/90 ph\u00fat, th\u00f4ng s\u1ed1 t\u01b0\u01a1ng t\u1ef1 c\u1ee7a Karius l\u00e0 1.63 c\u00f2n Mignolet ch\u1ec9 l\u00e0 1.54.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nKh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng c\u1ea3n ph\u00e1 c\u1ee7a Alisson \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 c\u1ef1c cao, theo \u0111\u00f3 t\u1ef7 l\u1ec7 c\u1ea3n ph\u00e1 nh\u1eefng c\u00fa d\u1ee9t \u0111i\u1ec3m \u0111i tr\u00fang khung th\u00e0nh c\u1ee7a anh l\u00ean t\u1edbi 79.3%. Th\u00f4ng s\u1ed1 n\u00e0y v\u01b0\u1ee3t tr\u1ed9i so v\u1edbi hai th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n c\u1ee7a Liverpool l\u00e0 Karius (67%) v\u00e0 Mignolet (57%).</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nX\u00e9t r\u1ed9ng ra, Alisson l\u00e0 th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n c\u00f3 kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng c\u1ea3n ph\u00e1 t\u1ed1t th\u1ee9 3 trong 5 gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u l\u1edbn nh\u1ea5t c\u1ee7a ch\u00e2u \u00c2u \u1edf m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i v\u1eeba r\u1ed3i. T\u1ef7 l\u1ec7 c\u1ea3n ph\u00e1 th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng 79.3% c\u1ee7a anh ch\u1ec9 x\u1ebfp sau David De Gea c\u1ee7a MU (80.2%) v\u00e0 Madrid Jan Oblak c\u1ee7a Atletico Madrid (82.7 %).</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>Alisson gi\u00fap Liverpool c\u00f3 th\u00eam c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i mang v\u1ec1 nh\u1eefng b\u00e0n th\u1eafng</h2>\r\n<h2>&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Liverpool s\u1edf h\u1eefu nh\u1eefng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng c\u00f3 t\u1ed1c \u0111\u1ed9 t\u1ed1t, h\u1ecd c\u00f3 chuy\u1ec3n tr\u1ea1ng th\u00e1i t\u1eeb ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ef1 sang t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng m\u1ed9t c\u00e1ch nhanh ch\u00f3ng.&nbsp;<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Alisson\" title=\"Alisson\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/19/Klopp-phat-bieu-ve-Liverpool-va-mo-vo-doi-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Alisson c\u00f3 kh\u1ea3 n\u0103n chuy\u1ec1n d\u00e0i c\u1ef1c t\u1ed1t</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nTrong m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 t\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng ph\u1ea3n c\u00f4ng nhanh, nh\u1eefng t\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng ph\u00e1t b\u00f3ng c\u1ee7a th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 m\u1edf ra c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i cho nh\u1eefng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng s\u1edf h\u1eefu t\u1ed1c \u0111\u1ed9 t\u1ed1t. Tuy nhi\u00ean, Liverpool kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nC\u1ea3 Mignolet v\u00e0 Karius \u0111\u1ec1u kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 cao v\u1ec1 kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng chuy\u1ec1n b\u00f3ng v\u00e0 chuy\u1ec1n d\u00e0i, t\u1ef7 l\u1ec7 chuy\u1ec1n b\u00f3ng th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng c\u1ee7a Karius \u1edf m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i v\u1eeba r\u1ed3i ch\u1ec9 \u1edf m\u1ee9c 67% c\u00f2n Mignolet ch\u1ec9 v\u00e0o kho\u1ea3ng 58%.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nTuy nhi\u00ean, v\u1edbi s\u1ef1 c\u00f3 m\u1eb7t c\u1ee7a Alisson, nh\u1eefng ng\u00f4i sao t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng c\u1ee7a Liverpool h\u1ee9a h\u1eb9n s\u1ebd c\u00f3 th\u00eam nh\u1eefng c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i \u0111\u1ec3 ghi b\u00e0n. Theo \u0111\u00f3, c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Brazil c\u00f3 kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng chuy\u1ec1n b\u00f3ng v\u00e0 ph\u00e1t b\u00f3ng d\u00e0i c\u1ef1c t\u1ed1t. M\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i v\u1eeba r\u1ed3i, t\u1ef7 l\u1ec7 chuy\u1ec1n b\u00f3ng ch\u00ednh x\u00e1c c\u1ee7a c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 26 tu\u1ed5i \u1edf Serie A 2017/18 v\u00e0o kho\u1ea3ng 79.7%.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nC\u0169ng \u1edf Serie A m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i v\u1eeba qua, Alisson \u0111\u00e3 ho\u00e0n th\u00e0nh nhi\u1ec1u \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng chuy\u1ec1n ch\u00ednh x\u00e1c h\u01a1n (1082) so v\u1edbi \u0111\u1ed3ng h\u01b0\u01a1ng Ederson (928), anh c\u0169ng l\u00e0 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 c\u00f3 t\u1ef7 l\u1ec7 chuy\u1ec1n d\u00e0i ch\u00ednh x\u00e1c nh\u1ea5t trong \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng th\u1ee7 \u0111\u00f4 Italia.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nKh\u00f4ng ch\u1ec9 c\u00f3 kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng ph\u1ea3n x\u1ea1 v\u00e0 chuy\u1ec1n d\u00e0i t\u1ed1t, Alisson c\u00f2n \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 cao v\u1ec1 kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng ph\u00e1n \u0111o\u00e1n v\u00e0 b\u1eaft b\u00e0i \u0111\u1ed1i ph\u01b0\u01a1ng. Trong m\u00e0u \u00e1o Roma, anh th\u01b0\u1eddng xuy\u00ean c\u00f3 nh\u1eefng t\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng b\u0103ng ra \u0111\u1ec3 b\u1eaft b\u00e0i nh\u1eefng \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng d\u00e0i t\u1eeb b\u00ean ph\u1ea7n s\u00e2n nh\u00e0 c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nV\u1edbi kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng ph\u00e1n \u0111o\u00e1n c\u1ef1c t\u1ed1t c\u1ee7a Alisson, anh c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 h\u1ea1n ch\u1ebf nh\u1eefng sai l\u1ea7m c\u1ee7a c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i. V\u1edbi nh\u1eefng t\u1ed1 ch\u1ea5t c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh, c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 26 tu\u1ed5i ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 ch\u1ee9ng t\u1ecf s\u1ed1 ti\u1ec1n 66 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng m\u00e0 Liverpool b\u1ecf ra \u0111\u1ec3 c\u00f3 anh l\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng h\u1ec1 \u0111\u1eaft.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/alisson-o-dau-khi-so-sanh-voi-nhung-thu-mon-hang-dau-ngoai-hang-anh-172-191526.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/18/alisson-o-dau-khi-so-sanh-voi-nhung-thu-mon-hang-dau-ngoai-hang-anh.png\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/alisson-o-dau-khi-so-sanh-voi-nhung-thu-mon-hang-dau-ngoai-hang-anh-172-191526.html\">Alisson \u1edf \u0111\u00e2u khi so s\u00e1nh v\u1edbi nh\u1eefng th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n h\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ea7u Ngo\u1ea1i h\u1ea1ng Anh?</span><br>\r\nChelsea mu\u1ed1n mua Alisson c\u1ee7a Roma trong tr\u01b0\u1eddng h\u1ee3p Courtois t\u1edbi Real, Liverpool c\u0169ng mu\u1ed1n c\u00f3 th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n 26 tu\u1ed5i thay Karius. C\u00f9ng so s\u00e1nh nh\u1eefng th\u00f4ng s\u1ed1 c\u1ee7a th\u1ee7...</div>\r\n</div>\r\nLiverpool \u0111ang s\u1edf h\u1eefu m\u1ed9t h\u00e0ng c\u00f4ng c\u1ef1c m\u1ea1nh, tuy\u1ebfn gi\u1eefa c\u1ee7a h\u1ecd c\u0169ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c n\u00e2ng c\u1ea5p b\u1edfi Naby Keita v\u00e0 Fabinho. V\u00e0 v\u1edbi s\u1ef1 c\u00f3 m\u1eb7t c\u1ee7a Alisson, h\u00e0ng th\u1ee7 Liverpool s\u1ebd \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c n\u00e2ng c\u1ea5p \u0111\u00e1ng k\u1ec3. V\u1edbi nh\u1eefng t\u00e2n binh ch\u1ea5t l\u01b0\u1ee3ng, L\u1eef \u0111o\u00e0n \u0111\u1ecf \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 c\u1ef1c cao \u1edf m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i t\u1edbi.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>\u0110\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh t\u1ed1i \u01b0u c\u1ee7a Liverpool \u1edf m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i 2018/19</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Doi hinh sieu khung cua Liverpool o mua giai toi\" title=\"\u0110\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh si\u00eau kh\u1ee7ng c\u1ee7a Liverpool \u1edf m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i t\u1edbi\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/19/doi.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\u0110\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh si\u00eau kh\u1ee7ng c\u1ee7a Liverpool \u1edf m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i t\u1edbi</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<h2>&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Nguy\u1ec5n Huy\u1ec1n (TTVN)</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"4380","checkdouble":"191614"},{"date":"17:54 19/07","title":"Sturridge n\u00f3i g\u00ec v\u1ec1 t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai b\u1ea5t \u0111\u1ecbnh \u1edf Liverpool?","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/19/sturridge-noi-gi-ve-tuong-lai-bat-dinh-o-liverpool.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Daniel Sturridge ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai, ng\u00f4i sao sinh n\u0103m 1989 kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh anh s\u1ebd kh\u00f4ng r\u1eddi s\u00e2n Anfield \u1edf k\u1ef3 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng H\u00e8 2018.\r\n</h2><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">T\u01b0\u01a1ng lai c\u1ee7a Daniel Sturridge \u1edf Liverpool v\u1eabn ch\u01b0a r\u00f5 r\u00e0ng</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nM\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i v\u1eeba qua, ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o Daniel Sturridge kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c tr\u1ecdng d\u1ee5ng trong m\u00e0u \u00e1o Liverpool. Ng\u00f4i sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi Anh ph\u1ea3i ng\u1ed3i d\u1ef1 b\u1ecb cho Roberto Firmino, khi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c HLV Klopp trao c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i anh c\u0169ng ch\u01a1i kh\u00f4ng m\u1ea5y \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Daniel Sturridge ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai \u1edf Liverpool h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Daniel Sturridge ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai \u1edf Liverpool h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/1/26/Daniel-Sturridge-phat-bieu-ve-tuong-lai-o-Liverpool-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>T\u01b0\u01a1ng lai Sturridge b\u1ecb \u0111\u1eb7t nhi\u1ec1u d\u1ea5u h\u1ecfi</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nV\u00e0o th\u00e1ng 1 n\u0103m nay, c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 29 tu\u1ed5i b\u1ecb Liverpool \u0111\u1ea9y t\u1edbi West Brom theo d\u1ea1ng cho m\u01b0\u1ee3n. Tuy nhi\u00ean, anh d\u00ednh ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u00e0 c\u0169ng kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c g\u00ec nhi\u1ec1u.</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n\u1ede th\u1eddi \u0111i\u1ec3m hi\u1ec7n t\u1ea1i <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/bong-da-anh/liverpool-tiet-lo-su-thuc-dau-long-tu-sturridge-172-189649.html\" target=\"_blank\">t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai Sturridge</span> \u0111ang b\u1ecb \u0111\u1eb7t r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u d\u1ea5u h\u1ecfi. V\u1edbi vi\u1ec7c kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u00f3ng g\u00f3p g\u00ec nhi\u1ec1u v\u00e0o l\u1ed1i ch\u01a1i c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng, Liverpool d\u1ef1 \u0111\u1ecbnh \u0111\u1ea9y ng\u00f4i sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi Anh ra \u0111i.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nThe Kop v\u1eabn c\u00f2n \u0111\u00f3 Solanke v\u00e0 Danny Ings, \u0111\u1ea5y l\u00e0 ch\u01b0a k\u1ec3 Origi tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i sau th\u1eddi gian cho m\u01b0\u1ee3n, b\u1edfi v\u1eady kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng Sturridge ra \u0111i l\u00e0 c\u1ef1c cao. Ng\u00f4i sao sinh n\u0103m 1989 c\u0169ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c cho l\u00e0 mu\u1ed1n r\u1eddi Anfield \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ra s\u00e2n nhi\u1ec1u h\u01a1n.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nHi\u1ec7n c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t v\u00e0i \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng \u1edf Anh quan t\u00e2m c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Anh. C\u1ee5 th\u1ec3, Everton, Southampton v\u00e0 Wolves l\u00e0 nh\u1eefng \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng mu\u1ed1n c\u00f3 ng\u00f4i sao 29 tu\u1ed5i.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>Sturridge l\u00ean ti\u1ebfng v\u1ec1 t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai</h2>\r\n<h2>\u00a0</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Daniel Sturridge ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai, ng\u00f4i sao sinh n\u0103m 1989 kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh anh s\u1ebd kh\u00f4ng r\u1eddi s\u00e2n Anfield \u1edf k\u1ef3 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng H\u00e8 2018.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Sturridge noi ve tuong lai\" title=\"Sturridge n\u00f3i v\u1ec1 t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/19/sturridge-noi-gi-ve-tuong-lai-bat-dinh-o-liverpool.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Sturridge n\u00f3i v\u1ec1 t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n\u201cT\u00f4i s\u1ebd ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c g\u1eafn b\u00f3 v\u1edbi Liverpool, hi\u1ec7n t\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n kh\u1ecfe m\u1ea1nh v\u00e0 s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng c\u1ea1nh tranh v\u1ecb tr\u00ed \u0111\u00e1 ch\u00ednh. T\u00f4i ngh\u0129 r\u1eb1ng n\u1ebfu \u0111\u1ea1t phong \u0111\u1ed9 t\u1ed1t t\u00f4i ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 ra s\u00e2n h\u00e0ng tu\u1ea7n, t\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 th\u1eddi gian \u0111\u00e1 t\u1ed1t t\u1ea1i Liverpool v\u00e0 mu\u1ed1n l\u1eb7p l\u1ea1i \u0111i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3 \u1edf m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i t\u1edbi\u201d.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n\u201cCh\u00fang t\u00f4i c\u00f3 nh\u1eefng tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u \u1edf M\u1ef9, Liverpool s\u1ebd \u0111\u1ee5ng \u0111\u1ed9 M.U, Man City v\u00e0 Dortmund. T\u00f4i ngh\u0129 r\u1eb1ng HLV s\u1ebd t\u1ea1o c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i cho c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh, t\u00f4i s\u1ebd c\u1ed1 g\u1eafng t\u1eadn d\u1ee5ng c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh \u0111\u1ec3 g\u00e2y \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng v\u1edbi \u00f4ng \u1ea5y\u201d.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nTrong 3 tr\u1eadn giao h\u1eefu c\u1ee7a Liverpool tr\u01b0\u1edbc Chester, Tranmere Rovers v\u00e0 Bury ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o Sturridge \u0111\u1ec1u \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng, c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 29 tu\u1ed5i ghi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c 2 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nL\u00ea H\u01b0\u1eddng (TTVN)</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"4379","checkdouble":"191615"},{"date":"17:27 19/07","title":"L\u1ecbch thi \u0111\u1ea5u giao h\u1eefu h\u00e8 2018 c\u1ee7a CLB Liverpool","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/original/2018/7/19/lich-thi-dau-giao-huu-he-2018-cua-clb-liverpool.jpeg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>L\u1ecbch thi \u0111\u1ea5u c\u1ee7a Liverpool trong m\u00f9a h\u00e8 2018: Chuy\u00ean trang Bongda24h c\u1eadp nh\u1eadt th\u00f4ng tin l\u1ecbch thi \u0111\u1ea5u - LT\u0110 giao h\u1eefu h\u00e8 2018 c\u1ee7a Liverpool nhanh v\u00e0 ch\u00ednh x\u00e1c nh\u1ea5t.</h2><div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"L\u1ecbch thi \u0111\u1ea5u c\u1ee7a Liverpool h\u00e8 2018 L\u1ecbch thi \u0111\u1ea5u h\u00e8 2018 Liverpool h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"L\u1ecbch thi \u0111\u1ea5u c\u1ee7a Liverpool h\u00e8 2018 L\u1ecbch thi \u0111\u1ea5u h\u00e8 2018 Liverpool h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/19/Lich-thi-dau-cua-Liverpool-he-2018-Lich-thi-dau-he-2018-Liverpool-hinh-anh.png\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">L\u1ecbch thi \u0111\u1ea5u giao h\u1eefu h\u00e8 2018 c\u1ee7a Liverpool</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: left;\">Liverpool l\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed9i b\u1ea1o chi nh\u1ea5t k\u1ec3 t\u1eeb \u0111\u1ea7u k\u1ef3 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng m\u00f9a h\u00e8 t\u1edbi nay. Sau khi gia c\u1ed1 tuy\u1ebfn gi\u1eefa b\u1eb1ng 2 t\u00e2n binh ch\u1ea5t l\u01b0\u1ee3ng l\u00e0 Naby Keita v\u00e0 Fabinho, Liverpool s\u1eafp s\u1eeda ho\u00e0n t\u1ea5t b\u1ea3n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng mua th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n Alisson Becker c\u1ee7a Roma v\u1edbi m\u1ee9c gi\u00e1 k\u1ef7 l\u1ee5c th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi d\u00e0nh cho th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n. <br>\r\n<br>\r\nTham v\u1ecdng c\u1ee7a L\u1eef \u0110o\u00e0n \u0110\u1ecf nh\u1eb1m t\u00ecm l\u1ea1i \u00e1nh h\u00e0o quang n\u0103m x\u01b0a l\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ea3i b\u00e0n c\u00e3i. \u0110\u1ec3 c\u00f3 s\u1ef1 chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb k\u1ef9 c\u00e0ng cho m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i m\u1edbi, \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng n\u00e0y c\u0169ng s\u1ebd c\u00f3 l\u1ecbch thi \u0111\u1ea5u n\u1eb7ng nh\u1ea5t khi tham d\u1ef1 t\u1ed5ng c\u1ed9ng 9 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u trong v\u00f2ng 33 ng\u00e0y, trung b\u00ecnh ch\u01b0a \u0111\u1ebfn 4 ng\u00e0y/tr\u1eadn. \u0110\u1ea7u ti\u00ean h\u1ecd s\u1ebd \u201ckh\u1edfi \u0111\u1ed9ng nh\u1eb9 nh\u00e0ng\u201d v\u1edbi 4 \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng chi\u1ebfu d\u01b0\u1edbi t\u1ea1i Anh.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nSau \u0111\u00f3 Liverpool se\u0303 di chuy\u00ea\u0309n sang My\u0303 \u0111\u00ea\u0309 tham d\u01b0\u0323 ICC 2018 \u0111\u00ea\u0309 cha\u0323m tra\u0301n Dortmund (22/7), Man City (25/7) va\u0300 M.U (28/7).</div>\r\n<h2>L\u1ecbch thi \u0111\u1ea5u c\u1ee7a Liverpool trong h\u00e8 2018</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: left;\">21h00 ng\u00e0y 7/7: Chester 0-7 Liverpool<br>\r\n01h30 ng\u00e0y 12/7: Tranmere 2-3 Liverpool<br>\r\n21h00 ng\u00e0y 14/7: Bury 0-0 Liverpool<br>\r\n01h45 ng\u00e0y 20/7: Blackburn Rovers vs Liverpool<br>\r\n03h05 ng\u00e0y 23/7:\u00a0 Liverpool vs Borussia Dortmund<br>\r\n07h05 ng\u00e0y 26/7: Man City vs Liverpool<br>\r\n04h05 ng\u00e0y 29/7: M.U vs Liverpool<br>\r\n00h00 ng\u00e0y 5/8: Liverpool vs Napoli<br>\r\n01h30 ng\u00e0y 8/8: Liverpool vs Torino</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<br></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"4378","checkdouble":"191616"},{"date":"09:15 19/07","title":"Perotti: \"Roma s\u1ebd s\u1ed1ng t\u1ed1t d\u00f9 m\u1ea5t Alisson v\u00e0o tay Liverpool\"","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Italia","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/original/2018/7/19/Klopp-phat-bieu-ve-Liverpool-va-mo-vo-doi-hinh-anh.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o Diego Perotti kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh Roma v\u1eabn s\u1ebd s\u1ed1ng t\u1ed1t k\u1ec3 c\u1ea3 khi m\u1ea5t \u0111i m\u1ed9t tr\u1ee5 c\u1ed9t quan tr\u1ecdng nh\u01b0 Alisson.</h2><h2>Alisson x\u00e1c nh\u1eadn r\u1eddi Roma</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/bong-da-anh/cuc-nong-liverpool-sap-co-alisson-voi-so-tien-sieu-khung-172-191535.html\" target=\"_blank\">Th\u1ee7 th\u00e0nh ng\u01b0\u1eddi Brazil \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c cho l\u00e0 chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb c\u1eadp b\u1ebfn Liverpool</span> v\u1edbi m\u1ee9c ph\u00ed chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng k\u1ef7 l\u1ee5c l\u00e0 67 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng sau khi tuy\u00ean b\u1ed1 mu\u1ed1n r\u1eddi Roma. Alisson \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c k\u1ef3 v\u1ecdng s\u1ebd k\u00fd v\u00e0o m\u1ed9t b\u1ea3n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng c\u00f3 th\u1eddi h\u1ea1n 6 n\u0103m v\u1edbi \u0111\u01b0\u01a1ng kim \u00e1 qu\u00e2n Champions League sau khi t\u1ecfa s\u00e1ng r\u1ef1c r\u1ee1 trong m\u00e0u \u00e1o Giallorossi m\u00f9a tr\u01b0\u1edbc.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u1ede m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i n\u0103m ngo\u00e1i, Alisson \u0111\u00e3 gi\u1eef s\u1ea1ch l\u01b0\u1edbi 28 l\u1ea7n sau 37 tr\u1eadn ra s\u00e2n cho Roma t\u1ea1i Serie A. C\u0169ng nh\u1edd v\u1eady m\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng \u00e1o b\u00e3 tr\u1ea7u c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 c\u00e1n \u0111\u00edch \u1edf v\u1ecb tr\u00ed th\u1ee9 3 chung cu\u1ed9c v\u00e0 c\u00f3 th\u1eddi \u0111i\u1ec3m c\u00f2n c\u1ea1nh tranh v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch v\u1edbi Juventus. Kh\u00f4ng nh\u1eefng th\u1ebf, s\u1ef1 xu\u1ea5t s\u1eafc c\u1ee7a ng\u00f4i sao 25 tu\u1ed5i c\u00f2n gi\u00fap \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng th\u1ee7 \u0111\u00f4 n\u01b0\u1edbc \u00dd l\u1ecdt v\u00e0o t\u1edbi tr\u1eadn b\u00e1n k\u1ebft Champions League.</div>\r\n<h2>Perotti tin t\u01b0\u1edfng v\u00e0o s\u1ee9c s\u1ed1ng m\u00e3nh li\u1ec7t c\u1ee7a Roma\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Perotti Roma s\u1ebd s\u1ed1ng t\u1ed1t d\u00f9 \u0111\u1ec3 Alisson t\u1edbi Liverpool h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Perotti Roma s\u1ebd s\u1ed1ng t\u1ed1t d\u00f9 \u0111\u1ec3 Alisson t\u1edbi Liverpool h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/19/Klopp-phat-bieu-ve-Liverpool-va-mo-vo-doi-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">\r\n            <h3>Perotti kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh Roma s\u1ebd s\u1ed1ng t\u1ed1t d\u00f9 m\u1ea5t th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n Alisson</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n</h2>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u1ede k\u1ef3 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng n\u00e0y, Roma \u0111\u00e3 m\u1ea5t Nainggolan v\u00e0o tay Inter. Trong khi \u0111\u00f3, Salah c\u0169ng chuy\u1ec3n t\u1edbi Liverpool m\u00f9a tr\u01b0\u1edbc. Nh\u01b0ng Perotti cho r\u1eb1ng \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng th\u1ee7 \u0111\u00f4 n\u01b0\u1edbc \u00dd ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 \u0111\u1ed1i ph\u00f3 v\u1edbi ho\u00e0n c\u1ea3nh kh\u00f3 kh\u0103n n\u00e0y.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<em>&ldquo;Alisson l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n quan tr\u1ecdng v\u1edbi ch\u00fang t\u00f4i. Nh\u1eefng pha c\u1ee9u thua c\u1ee7a c\u1eadu \u1ea5y gi\u00fap ch\u00fang t\u00f4i ki\u1ebfm \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c nhi\u1ec1u \u0111i\u1ec3m s\u1ed1 \u1edf m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i n\u0103m ngo\u00e1i. Nh\u01b0ng <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/\" title=\"bong da\" type=\"bong da\">b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 </span>l\u00e0 nh\u01b0 v\u1eady.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n&ldquo;T\u00f4i mu\u1ed1n n\u00f3i l\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng n\u00e0o t\u1ef1 h\u1ee7y ho\u1ea1i m\u00ecnh c\u1ea3. M\u1ed7i b\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111i \u0111\u1ec1u \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c th\u1ef1c hi\u1ec7n \u0111\u1ec3 gi\u00fap c\u1ea3i thi\u1ec7n s\u1ee9c m\u1ea1nh c\u1ee7a to\u00e0n \u0111\u1ed9i. Ch\u00fang ta s\u1ebd c\u00f9ng xem Roma \u0111\u1ee9ng \u1edf \u0111\u00e2u v\u00e0o cu\u1ed1i m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i n\u00e0y.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n&ldquo;Ph\u1ea3i th\u1eeba nh\u1eadn Alisson l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t s\u1ef1 m\u1ea5t m\u00e1t l\u1edbn v\u1edbi ch\u00fang t\u00f4i. C\u1eadu \u1ea5y l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t ch\u00e0ng trai t\u1ed1t v\u00e0 c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t c\u00e1 t\u00ednh m\u1ea1nh trong ph\u00f2ng thay \u0111\u1ed3. Ch\u00fang t\u00f4i ti\u1ebfc v\u00ec c\u1eadu \u1ea5y ra \u0111i nh\u01b0ng cu\u1ed9c s\u1ed1ng lu\u00f4n thay \u0111\u1ed5i m\u00e0.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n&ldquo;Ch\u00fang t\u00f4i c\u0169ng \u0111\u00e3 m\u1ea5t Salah v\u00e0 Nainggolan. Nh\u01b0ng Roma s\u1ebd b\u01b0\u1edbc ti\u1ebfp. V\u00e0 ch\u00fang t\u00f4i c\u1ea7n ph\u1ea3i ch\u01a1i t\u1ed1t nh\u01b0 nh\u1eefng g\u00ec \u0111\u00e3 l\u00e0m \u1edf m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i n\u0103m ngo\u00e1i&rdquo;.</em><br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u1ede k\u1ef3 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng n\u00e0y, Roma \u0111\u00e3 mang v\u1ec1 r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u c\u00e1i t\u00ean tr\u1ebb v\u00e0 t\u00e0i n\u0103ng. \u0110\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng \u00e1o b\u00e3 tr\u1ea7u c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t m\u00f9a h\u00e8 kh\u00e1 b\u1eadn r\u1ed9n khi \u0111\u00e3 chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng t\u1edbi 7 t\u00e2n binh: Javier Pastore, Justin Kluivert, Ante Coric, Davide Santon, Nicolo Zaniolo, William Bianda v\u00e0 Antonio Mirante.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Xem th\u00eam nh\u1eefng tin t\u1ee9c kh\u00e1c v\u1ec1 Roma:</strong><br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/nong-alisson-xac-nhan-roi-roma-toi-liverpool-voi-gia-sieu-khung-172-191549.html\">N\u00f3ng: Alisson x\u00e1c nh\u1eadn r\u1eddi Roma t\u1edbi Liverpool v\u1edbi gi\u00e1 si\u00eau kh\u1ee7ng</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/alisson-o-dau-khi-so-sanh-voi-nhung-thu-mon-hang-dau-ngoai-hang-anh-172-191526.html\">Alisson \u1edf \u0111\u00e2u khi so s\u00e1nh v\u1edbi nh\u1eefng th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n h\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ea7u Ngo\u1ea1i h\u1ea1ng Anh?</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Xu\u00e2n Phong (TTVN)</strong></div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"4377","checkdouble":"191568"},{"date":"11:01 19/07","title":"\u0110\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 c\u1ee7a U19 Vi\u1ec7t Nam t\u1ea1i gi\u1ea3i t\u1ee9 h\u00f9ng: \u0110\u00e0n em Luis Suarez v\u00e0 Drogba","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Vi\u1ec7t Nam","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/original/2018/7/7/doi-thu-cua-u19-viet-nam-tai-giai-tu-hung-dan-em-luis-suarez.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>U19 Vi\u1ec7t Nam s\u1ebd g\u1eb7p th\u00e1ch th\u1ee9c r\u1ea5t l\u1edbn khi ch\u1ea1m tr\u00e1n v\u1edbi nh\u1eefng \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 m\u1ea1nh t\u1ea1i gi\u1ea3i giao h\u1eefu t\u1ee9 h\u00f9ng Qatar \u0111\u1ec3 chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb cho VCK U19 ch\u00e2u \u00c1.</h2><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">U19 Vi\u1ec7t Nam d\u1ef1 gi\u1ea3i t\u1ee9 h\u00f9ng<br>\r\n\u00a0</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u0110\u1ec3 chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb cho VCK U19 ch\u00e2u \u00c1 2018, U19 Vi\u1ec7t Nam \u0111\u00e3 nh\u1eadn l\u1eddi tham d\u1ef1 gi\u1ea3i giao h\u1eefu t\u1ee9 h\u00f9ng Qatar. \u0110\u00e2y l\u00e0 gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ch\u1ee7 nh\u00e0 Qatar t\u1ed5 ch\u1ee9c t\u1ea1i Doha t\u1eeb 16-23/9 nh\u1eb1m t\u1ea1o c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i c\u1ecd x\u00e1t cho U19 Qatar tr\u01b0\u1edbc th\u1ec1m VCK U19 ch\u00e2u \u00c1.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"\u0110\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 c\u1ee7a U19 Vi\u1ec7t Nam t\u1ea1i gi\u1ea3i t\u1ee9 h\u00f9ng \u0110\u00e0n em Luis Suarez  h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"\u0110\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 c\u1ee7a U19 Vi\u1ec7t Nam t\u1ea1i gi\u1ea3i t\u1ee9 h\u00f9ng \u0110\u00e0n em Luis Suarez  h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/7/doi-thu-cua-u19-viet-nam-tai-giai-tu-hung-dan-em-luis-suarez.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\u0110\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 c\u1ee7a U19 Vi\u1ec7t Nam t\u1ea1i gi\u1ea3i t\u1ee9 h\u00f9ng ngo\u00e0i ch\u1ee7 nh\u00e0 Qatar c\u00f2n c\u00f3 Uruguay v\u00e0 B\u1edd Bi\u1ec3n Ng\u00e0.</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nNgo\u00e0i ch\u1ee7 nh\u00e0 U19 Qatar s\u1ebd tri\u1ec7u t\u1eadp nhi\u1ec1u c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 \u0111ang \u0103n t\u1eadp \u1edf ch\u00e2u \u00c2u, U19 Vi\u1ec7t Nam s\u1ebd g\u1eb7p hai \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 c\u1ef1c m\u1ea1nh kh\u00e1c l\u00e0 U19 Uruguay v\u00e0 U19 B\u1edd Bi\u1ec3n Ng\u00e0. T\u1ea1i VCK U20 World Cup 2017, U20 Uruguay khi \u0111\u00f3 \u0111\u00e3 gi\u00e0nh v\u1ecb tr\u00ed th\u1ee9 t\u01b0 chung cu\u1ed9c.\u00a0<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Vi\u1ec7c ph\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ed1i m\u1eb7t v\u1edbi nh\u1eefng \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 m\u1ea1nh, c\u00f3 nhi\u1ec1u phong c\u00e1ch thi \u0111\u1ea5u kh\u00e1c nhau l\u00e0 c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i \u0111\u1ec3 U19 Vi\u1ec7t Nam c\u00f3 s\u1ef1 chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb t\u1ed1t nh\u1ea5t tr\u01b0\u1edbc khi b\u01b0\u1edbc v\u00e0o VCK U19 ch\u00e2u \u00c1.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">Hy v\u1ecdng t\u1ea1i VCK U19 ch\u00e2u \u00c1<br>\r\n\u00a0</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">T\u1ea1i VCK U19 ch\u00e2u \u00c1 di\u1ec5n ra v\u00e0o hai n\u0103m tr\u01b0\u1edbc, th\u1ea7y tr\u00f2 HLV Ho\u00e0ng Anh Tu\u1ea5n t\u1eebng g\u00e2y b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd khi ti\u1ebfn v\u00e0o b\u00e1n k\u1ebft, qua \u0111\u00f3 gi\u00e0nh su\u1ea5t d\u1ef1 VCK U20 World Cup 2017. V\u00ec v\u1eady \u1edf gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u l\u1ea7n n\u00e0y, U19 Vi\u1ec7t Nam \u0111\u1eb7t m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau t\u00e1i l\u1eadp th\u00e0nh t\u00edch c\u1ee7a hai n\u0103m tr\u01b0\u1edbc.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">HLV Ho\u00e0ng Anh Tu\u1ea5n cho r\u1eb1ng U19 Vi\u1ec7t Nam ph\u1ea3i d\u00e1m m\u01a1 th\u00ec m\u1edbi \u0111\u1ea1t \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau: \"\u0110\u1ec3 t\u00e1i l\u1eadp th\u00e0nh t\u00edch \u0111\u00f3 ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn kh\u00f4ng d\u1ec5 d\u00e0ng, nh\u01b0ng ch\u00fang ta ph\u1ea3i c\u00f3 m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau \u0111\u1ec3 ph\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ea5u v\u00e0 chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb. D\u00f9 kh\u00f3 nh\u01b0ng kh\u00f4ng g\u00ec l\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3\".<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">VCK U19 ch\u00e2u \u00c1 2018 s\u1ebd di\u1ec5n ra t\u1eeb 18/10 - 4/11 t\u1ea1i Indonesia. \u0110T U19 Vi\u1ec7t Nam s\u1ebd n\u1eb1m \u1edf b\u1ea3ng C v\u1edbi nh\u1eefng \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 r\u1ea5t kh\u00f3 l\u00e0 U19 Australia, U19 H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c v\u00e0 U19 Jordan.\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>Xem th\u00eam nh\u1eefng b\u00e0i vi\u1ebft kh\u00e1c tr\u00ean Bongda24h.vn v\u1ec1 U19 Vi\u1ec7t Nam:</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/hlv-hoang-anh-tuan-noi-gi-sau-that-bai-cua-u19-viet-nam-tai-giai-u19-dna-168-190845.html\">HLV Ho\u00e0ng Anh Tu\u1ea5n n\u00f3i g\u00ec sau th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i c\u1ee7a U19 Vi\u1ec7t Nam t\u1ea1i gi\u1ea3i U19 \u0110N\u00c1?</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/truc-tiep-bong-da/u19-viet-nam-vs-u19-singapore-ngay-hom-nay-97-372-190790.html\">U19 Vi\u1ec7t Nam 2-2 U19 Singapore (KT): Chia tay gi\u1ea3i U19 \u0110\u00f4ng Nam \u00c1 2018 trong n\u1ed7i th\u1ea5t v\u1ecdng</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/doi-gio-thi-dau-u19-viet-nam-con-co-hoi-vuot-qua-vong-bang-u19-dna-168-190749.html\">\u0110\u1ed5i gi\u1edd thi \u0111\u1ea5u, U19 Vi\u1ec7t Nam c\u00f2n c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i v\u01b0\u1ee3t qua v\u00f2ng b\u1ea3ng U19 \u0110N\u00c1</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/u19-viet-nam-co-nguy-co-bi-loai-hlv-hoang-anh-tuan-noi-gi-168-190686.html\">U19 Vi\u1ec7t Nam c\u00f3 nguy c\u01a1 b\u1ecb lo\u1ea1i, HLV Ho\u00e0ng Anh Tu\u1ea5n n\u00f3i g\u00ec?</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/truc-tiep-bong-da/u19-viet-nam-vs-u19-indonesia-ngay-hom-nay-372-190607.html\">U19 Vi\u1ec7t Nam 0-1 U19 Indonesia (KT): T\u00ednh to\u00e1n sai l\u1ea7m, th\u1ea7y tr\u00f2 Ho\u00e0ng Anh Tu\u1ea5n nh\u1eadn th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i cay \u0111\u1eafng</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/u19-viet-nam-thoai-mai-tam-ly-truoc-tran-cau-sinh-tu-voi-u19-indonesia-168-190579.html\">U19 Vi\u1ec7t Nam tho\u1ea3i m\u00e1i t\u00e2m l\u00fd tr\u01b0\u1edbc tr\u1eadn c\u1ea7u sinh t\u1eed v\u1edbi U19 Indonesia</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong>N.D (TTVN)</strong></div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"4376","checkdouble":"191582"},{"date":"10:13 19/07","title":"Barca s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ed5i ng\u00f4i sao \u0111\u1eaft gi\u00e1 l\u1ea5y Hazard","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Ch\u00e2u \u00c2u","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/original/2018/5/21/barca-doi-dembele-lay-hazard.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Barcelona \u0111\u00e3 s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng g\u00e1n Ousmane Dembele v\u00e0o h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ec3 chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 Eden Hazard t\u1eeb Chelsea ngay h\u00e8 n\u00e0y.</h2><h2>Hazard \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c s\u0103n \u0111\u00f3n</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Eden <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/bong-da-anh/nong-hazard-dich-than-tuyen-bo-muon-roi-chelsea-172-191203.html\" target=\"_blank\">Hazard \u0111\u00e3 b\u00e0y t\u1ecf mong mu\u1ed1n r\u1eddi kh\u1ecfi Stamford Bridge</span> h\u00e8 n\u00e0y. Ng\u00f4i sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi B\u1ec9 c\u0169ng \u00fap m\u1edf r\u1eb1ng Real Madrid l\u00e0 \u0111i\u1ec3m \u0111\u1ebfn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c anh \u01b0u ti\u00ean.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nH\u1ed3i \u0111\u1ea7u tu\u1ea7n n\u00e0y, nh\u1eefng tin \u0111\u1ed3n t\u1eeb Ph\u00e1p cho th\u1ea5y Hazard \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u1ea1t th\u1ecfa thu\u1eadn mi\u1ec7ng v\u1edbi Real Madrid. \u0110\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng ho\u00e0ng gia T\u00e2y Ban Nha b\u00e2y gi\u1edd ch\u1ec9 c\u1ea7n ph\u1ea3i \u0111\u00e0m ph\u00e1n \u0111\u1ec3 th\u1ed1ng nh\u1ea5t m\u1ee9c ph\u00ed chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng v\u1edbi Chelsea.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Dembele Hazard\" title=\"Dembele Hazard\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/19/100030-3.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">\r\n            <h3>Barca mu\u1ed1n \u0111\u1ed5i Dembele l\u1ea5y Hazard</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n\u0110\u01b0\u1ee3c bi\u1ebft, Barcelona c\u0169ng r\u1ea5t quan t\u00e2m t\u1edbi ng\u00f4i sao 27 tu\u1ed5i. V\u00e0 c\u0169ng \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 tin \u0111\u1ed3n cho th\u1ea5y nh\u00e0 \u0110KV\u0110 T\u00e2y Ban Nha \u0111ang b\u1eaft \u0111\u1ea7u \u0111\u00e0m ph\u00e1n v\u1edbi ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u1ea1i di\u1ec7n c\u1ee7a Hazard.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nChelsea l\u00fac n\u00e0y v\u1eabn \u0111ang n\u1eafm \u0111\u1eb1ng chu\u00f4i v\u1ee5 Hazard. C\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi B\u1ec9 hi\u1ec7n c\u00f2n 2 n\u0103m h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng v\u1edbi The Blues v\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 s\u00e2n Stamford Bridge s\u1ebd \u0111\u01b0a ra quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh cu\u1ed1i c\u00f9ng.</div>\r\n<h2>Barca g\u1eedi l\u1eddi \u0111\u1ec1 ngh\u1ecb kh\u1ee7ng</h2>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Theo truy\u1ec1n th\u00f4ng T\u00e2y Ban Nha, Barcelona \u0111\u00e3 b\u1eaft \u0111\u1ea7u th\u1eed th\u00e1ch s\u1ef1 ki\u00ean nh\u1eabn c\u1ee7a Chelsea b\u1eb1ng vi\u1ec7c \u0111\u01b0a sao tr\u1ebb t\u00e0i n\u0103ng Ousmane Dembele v\u00e0o h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 Hazard.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nBarca \u0111\u00e3 k\u00fd h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng v\u1edbi Dembele m\u00f9a h\u00e8 n\u0103m ngo\u00e1i v\u1edbi m\u1ee9c ph\u00ed chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng l\u00ean \u0111\u1ebfn 96.8 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng. Con s\u1ed1 n\u00e0y c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 t\u0103ng l\u00ean 135.5 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng t\u00f9y thu\u1ed9c v\u00e0o th\u00e0nh t\u00edch c\u1ee7a c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Ph\u00e1p.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nNh\u01b0ng sao tr\u1ebb 21 tu\u1ed5i \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i ra m\u1eaft \u0111\u00e1ng qu\u00ean t\u1ea1i Camp Nou. L\u00fac n\u00e0y, anh c\u0169ng \u0111ang b\u1ecb g\u1eafn v\u1edbi nh\u1eefng tin \u0111\u1ed3n chia tay Barca.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nD\u1eabu v\u1eady, Chelsea v\u1eabn kh\u00e1 quy\u1ebft t\u00e2m trong vi\u1ec7c ng\u0103n Hazard r\u1eddi kh\u1ecfi Stamford Bridge. Hi\u1ec7n t\u1ea1i, \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng th\u00e0nh London c\u0169ng \u0111\u1ee9ng tr\u01b0\u1edbc nguy c\u01a1 m\u1ea5t m\u1ed9t ng\u00f4i sao t\u1ea7m c\u1ee1 kh\u00e1c l\u00e0 Thibaut Courtois.<br>\r\nXu\u00e2n Phong (TTVN)</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"4375","checkdouble":"191575"},{"date":"09:42 19/07","title":"\u0110\u00e2y! S\u1ed1 ti\u1ec1n kh\u1ee7ng Real r\u00f3t v\u00e0o chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng h\u00e8 n\u00e0y","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 TBN","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/original/2018/7/19/real-chi-400-trieu-euro-vao-chuyen-nhuong-he-nay.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Real chi 300 tri\u1ec7u Euro v\u00e0o chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng h\u00e8 n\u00e0y. \u0110\u1ee9ng \u0111\u1ea7u trong danh s\u00e1ch c\u1ea7n tuy\u1ec3n m\u1ed9 c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng Ho\u00e0ng gia T\u00e2y Ban Nha kh\u00f4ng ai kh\u00e1c ngo\u00e0i b\u1ed9 \u0111\u00f4i Courtois v\u00e0 Hazard c\u1ee7a Chelsea.\r\n</h2><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nCh\u1ee7 t\u1ecbch Perez h\u1ee9a \u201cph\u00e1 k\u00e9t\u201d</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nNgay sau chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng Liverpool \u1edf chung k\u1ebft Champions League m\u00f9a 2017/18, Cristiano Ronaldo \u0111\u00e3 b\u00f3ng gi\u00f3 s\u1ebd r\u1eddi Real Madrid. R\u1ed1t c\u1ee5c, \u0111i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3 \u0111\u00e3 tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh s\u1ef1 th\u1eadt sau khi ng\u00f4i sao 33 tu\u1ed5i chuy\u1ec3n sang Juventus v\u1edbi m\u1ee9c gi\u00e1 l\u00ean \u0111\u1ebfn 112 tri\u1ec7u Euro.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nKh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 ch\u00e2n s\u00fat ghi trung b\u00ecnh 50 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng/ m\u00f9a ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t thi\u1ec7t th\u00f2i. V\u00e0 Real bu\u1ed9c l\u00f2ng ph\u1ea3i b\u1eaft tay v\u00e0o th\u1ecb tr\u01b0\u1eddng chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng v\u00e0 mang v\u1ec1 nh\u1eefng ng\u00f4i sao thay th\u1ebf.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Real chi 300 tri\u1ec7u Euro v\u00e0o chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng h\u00e8 n\u00e0y h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Real chi 300 tri\u1ec7u Euro v\u00e0o chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng h\u00e8 n\u00e0y h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/19/real-chi-400-trieu-euro-vao-chuyen-nhuong-he-nay.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">Perez h\u1ee9a s\u1ebd mang v\u1ec1 nh\u1eefng c\u00e1i t\u00ean x\u1ee9ng t\u1ea7m</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nCh\u1ee7 t\u1ecbch Florentino Perez c\u0169ng kh\u00f4ng gi\u1ea5u gi\u1ebfm \u00fd \u0111\u1ecbnh n\u00e0y. Trong m\u1ed9t ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u m\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y nh\u00e2n l\u1ec5 ra m\u1eaft c\u1ee7a t\u00e2n binh 40 tri\u1ec7u Euro Alvaro Odriozola, ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u1ee9ng \u0111\u1ea7u Real kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh s\u1ebd t\u0103ng c\u01b0\u1eddng l\u1ef1c l\u01b0\u1ee3ng m\u1ea1nh m\u1ebd trong th\u1eddi gian t\u1edbi.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>Chi 300 tri\u1ec7u Euro cho 4 ng\u00f4i sao</h2>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nV\u1edbi vi\u1ec7c Zinedine Zidane t\u1eeb ch\u1ee9c, Real nhanh ch\u00f3ng m\u1eddi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c Julen Lopetegui tr\u00e1m ch\u1ed7 HLV tr\u01b0\u1edfng. V\u00e0 sau cu\u1ed9c h\u1ecdp c\u00f9ng thuy\u1ec1n tr\u01b0\u1edfng m\u1edbi, quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c Perez c\u00f9ng c\u1ed9ng s\u1ef1 \u0111\u01b0a ra: Real chi 300 tri\u1ec7u Euro v\u00e0o chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng h\u00e8 n\u00e0y cho 4 c\u00e1i t\u00ean.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Eden Hazard\" title=\"Eden Hazard\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/11/real-san-sang-chi-150-trieu-bang-de-mua-hazard.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">\r\n            <h3>Real chi 300 tri\u1ec7u Euro v\u00e0o chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng h\u00e8 n\u00e0y v\u00e0 Hazard n\u1eb1m trong \u0111\u00f3</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n\u0110\u1ea7u ti\u00ean, ng\u01b0\u1eddi thay Ronaldo s\u1ebd l\u00e0 Eden Hazard, ng\u01b0\u1eddi b\u00e0y t\u1ecf mong mu\u1ed1n r\u1eddi Chelsea h\u00e8 n\u00e0y. Tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u00f3, Real nh\u1eafm Neymar v\u00e0 Kylian Mbappe song v\u01b0\u1edbng ph\u1ea3i s\u1ef1 c\u1ee9ng r\u1eafn t\u1edbi t\u1eeb \u0111\u1ea1i gia PSG. \u0110i k\u00e8m v\u1edbi \u0111\u00f3, h\u1ecd c\u1ed1 g\u1eafng \u0111\u01b0a v\u1ec1 th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n Thibaut Courtois, ng\u01b0\u1eddi ch\u1ec9 c\u00f2n 1 n\u0103m h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng v\u1edbi Chelsea.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nK\u1ebf \u0111\u1ebfn l\u00e0 v\u1ecb tr\u00ed trung v\u1ec7, n\u01a1i Real ch\u1ec9 c\u00f3 2 c\u00e1i t\u00ean \u0111\u00e1ng tin c\u1eady l\u00e0 Sergio Ramos v\u00e0 Raphael Varane. Los Blancos t\u00ednh ch\u01a1i l\u1edbn v\u1edbi Leonardo Bonucci, m\u1ed9t t\u00ean tu\u1ed5i \u0111\u1eb3ng c\u1ea5p th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi song kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c s\u1ef1 h\u00f2a nh\u1eadp t\u1ed1t v\u1edbi AC Milan.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nCu\u1ed1i c\u00f9ng, Real s\u1ebd g\u00f5 c\u1eeda Juventus, \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng m\u00e0 h\u1ecd m\u1edbi nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng l\u1ea1i Ronaldo. HLV Lopetegui mu\u1ed1n c\u00f3 ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 trung t\u00e2m Miralem Pjanic. \u0110\u00e2y \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c xem l\u00e0 s\u1ef1 k\u1ebf th\u1eeba cho Luka Modric s\u1ebd b\u01b0\u1edbc sang tu\u1ed5i 33 v\u00e0o th\u00e1ng 9 t\u1edbi.<br>\r\n<strong><br>\r\nXem th\u00eam m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 b\u00e0i vi\u1ebft v\u1ec1 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng Real tr\u00ean Bongda24h.vn:<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/tin-chuyen-nhuong/chu-tich-la-liga-tiet-lo-ly-do-ronaldo-chia-tay-real-187-191544.html\">Ch\u1ee7 t\u1ecbch La Liga ti\u1ebft l\u1ed9 l\u00fd do Ronaldo chia tay Real</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-tbn/goc-real-madrid-4-cai-ten-huong-loi-nhat-duoi-thoi-lopetegui-180-191534.html\">G\u00f3c Real Madrid: 4 c\u00e1i t\u00ean h\u01b0\u1edfng l\u1ee3i nh\u1ea5t d\u01b0\u1edbi th\u1eddi Lopetegui</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/3-ly-do-tin-tuong-real-madrid-se-chieu-mo-thanh-cong-eden-hazard-172-191533.html\">3 l\u00fd do tin t\u01b0\u1edfng Real Madrid s\u1ebd chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng Eden Hazard</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-tbn/theo-hernandez-sap-roi-real-180-191512.html\">L\u1ed9 di\u1ec7n ng\u00f4i sao ti\u1ebfp theo chia tay Real Madrid?</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/alisson-o-dau-khi-so-sanh-voi-nhung-thu-mon-hang-dau-ngoai-hang-anh-172-191526.html\">Alisson \u1edf \u0111\u00e2u khi so s\u00e1nh v\u1edbi nh\u1eefng th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n h\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ea7u Ngo\u1ea1i h\u1ea1ng Anh?</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<br>\r\nGia Vi (TTVN)</strong><br>\r\n\u00a0</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"4374","checkdouble":"191579"}]}